86	Call of Duty NEXT, kadoron pehldka budoucnosti srie Call of Duty, odhalila zsadn zmny, kter ekaj Warzone v nsledujcch mscch.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"4reub\\"><b>S p\\u0159\\u00edchodem Black Ops 6 se hr\\u00e1\\u010di Warzone mohou t\\u011b\\u0161it na zbrusu novou mapu, p\\u0159epracovan\\u00e9 hern\\u00ed mechaniky a \\u0159adu dal\\u0161\\u00edch vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed, kter\\u00e1 slibuj\\u00ed o\\u017eivit battle royale ve h\\u0159e.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"a77rb\\"><b>Warzone \\u010dekaj\\u00ed zm\\u011bny</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"1t662\\">Jednou z nejv\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00edch novinek je mapa <b>Area 99</b>, kter\\u00e1 se to\\u010d\\u00ed kolem jadern\\u00e9 elektr\\u00e1rny a tematicky navazuje na ikonickou mapu <b>Nuketown</b> z Black Ops. Velkou zpr\\u00e1vou tak\\u00e9 je, \\u017ee se v p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00edm roce vr\\u00e1t\\u00ed legend\\u00e1rn\\u00ed mapa <b>Verdansk</b>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"2kcrf\\">S vyd\\u00e1n\\u00edm <b>Black Ops 6</b> se Warzone do\\u010dk\\u00e1 tak\\u00e9 implementace nov\\u00e9 mechaniky pohybu <i>Omnimovement</i>, kter\\u00e1 hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm nab\\u00eddne v\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed svobodu a dynamiku v boji. Samoz\\u0159ejmost\\u00ed je tak\\u00e9 p\\u0159enos v\\u0161ech zbran\\u00ed a v\\u011bt\\u0161iny vybaven\\u00ed z <b>Black Ops 6</b> do Warzone.</p><p data-block-key=\\"5m86a\\">D\\u00edky mechanismu C<i>arry Forward </i>se do Warzone dostanou t\\u00e9m\\u011b\\u0159 v\\u0161echny zbran\\u011b z MWII a MWIII. Novinkou je tak\\u00e9 mo\\u017enost n\\u00e9st do Warzone zbra\\u0148 na bl\\u00edzko jako t\\u0159et\\u00ed volbu. </p><p data-block-key=\\"9b9rq\\">Co se t\\u00fd\\u010de perk\\u016f, hr\\u00e1\\u010di si budou moci vybrat t\\u0159i perky, kter\\u00e9 si vezmou do Warzone, a tak\\u00e9 <i>Wildcard</i>, kter\\u00fd nebyl v r\\u00e1mci Call of Duty k vid\\u011bn\\u00ed n\\u011bkolik let. Pro milovn\\u00edky v\\u00fdzev zas <b>Activision</b> p\\u0159ipravil v Warzone hromadu nov\\u00fdch \\u00fakol\\u016f. </p><p data-block-key=\\"6udgc\\">A aby toho nebylo m\\u00e1lo, <b>Raven Software</b> se rozhodl zbavit se t\\u011b\\u017ekop\\u00e1dn\\u00fdch batoh\\u016f a vr\\u00e1tit spr\\u00e1vu invent\\u00e1\\u0159e k z\\u00e1klad\\u016fm. V\\u0161e, co pot\\u0159ebujete, najdete tak v p\\u0159ehledn\\u00e9m menu. Do hry se v\\u0161ak vracej\\u00ed bra\\u0161ny, kter\\u00e9 v\\u00e1m umo\\u017en\\u00ed n\\u00e9st v\\u00edce panc\\u00e9\\u0159ov\\u00fdch pl\\u00e1t\\u016f nebo munice.  Raven tak\\u00e9 vylep\\u0161il \\u0159adu hern\\u00edch mechanik spojen\\u00fdch s pohybem a funkcemi pro zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed kvality \\u017eivota.  </p>", "id": "6f32b4ae-9687-4739-9e02-cee3950e8e87"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "028e65b3-b18f-44f0-bf94-09e46bc8f0c6"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"4reub\\">S prvn\\u00ed sez\\u00f3nou Black Ops 6 a Warzone doraz\\u00ed hodnocen\\u00fd re\\u017eim Battle Royale, kter\\u00fd jist\\u011b pot\\u011b\\u0161\\u00ed sout\\u011b\\u017eiv\\u00e9 hr\\u00e1\\u010de. Call of Duty: Warzone se tak chyst\\u00e1 na po\\u0159\\u00e1dnou explozi nov\\u00e9ho obsahu.</p><p data-block-key=\\"2qbiu\\"><b>Call of Duty: Black Ops 6</b> vych\\u00e1z\\u00ed ji\\u017e 25. \\u0159\\u00edjna leto\\u0161n\\u00edho roku na PC a konzole star\\u00e9 i nov\\u00e9 generace.</p><p data-block-key=\\"95v1p\\"><b>Jak se t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edte na nov\\u00fd d\\u00edl Call of Duty: Black Ops 6? Hrajete Warzone? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f nebo na\\u0161e soci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed s\\u00edt\\u011b.</b></p>", "id": "7d859944-d07f-413e-a8b2-3ec0c7a2712e"}]	717	48	warzone, call of duty, cod, black ops 6, update, verdansk	\N	1	0	0
98	Vvoji z Funcomu piznvaj, e penst jejich ambicizn MMO hru Dune: Awakening na Xbox Series S je pro n skuten nron.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"4zbzo\\"><b>Xbox Series S se st\\u00e1v\\u00e1 p\\u0159ek\\u00e1\\u017ekou pro n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159e. Funcom p\\u0159izn\\u00e1v\\u00e1, \\u017ee p\\u0159en\\u00e9st Dune: Awakening na tuto konzoli je pro n\\u011b v\\u00fdzvou. </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"fdvv5\\"><b>Dune: Awakening zaznamen\\u00e1v\\u00e1 probl\\u00e9m na konzoli Xbox Series S</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"9afkt\\"><b>Dune: Awakening</b>, MMO survival hra zasazen\\u00e1 do sv\\u011bta <b>Duny</b>, slibuje hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm mo\\u017enost prozkoum\\u00e1vat pou\\u0161t\\u011b <b>Arrakisu</b>, sb\\u00edrat ko\\u0159en\\u00ed, vyr\\u00e1b\\u011bt p\\u0159edm\\u011bty a bojovat o moc. Hr\\u00e1\\u010di budou moci zakl\\u00e1dat vlastn\\u00ed rody a budovat sv\\u00e9 imp\\u00e9rium.</p><p data-block-key=\\"4i77j\\">S tak ambici\\u00f3zn\\u00edm projektem je pochopiteln\\u00e9, \\u017ee slab\\u0161\\u00ed hardware <b>Xbox Series S </b>p\\u0159edstavuje pro v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159e z Funcomu v\\u00fdzvu. Cht\\u011bj\\u00ed, aby hra vypadala skv\\u011ble na v\\u0161ech platform\\u00e1ch, ani\\u017e by museli ob\\u011btovat kvalitu nebo obsah.</p><p data-block-key=\\"7t125\\">Scott Junor, produktov\\u00fd \\u0159editel Funcomu, uvedl, \\u017ee se zam\\u011b\\u0159uj\\u00ed na optimalizaci hern\\u00edch prvk\\u016f a vyu\\u017e\\u00edv\\u00e1n\\u00ed technologi\\u00ed, jako je<b> FSR</b>, aby dos\\u00e1hli co nejlep\\u0161\\u00edch v\\u00fdsledk\\u016f. C\\u00edlem je, aby hra vypadala \\u00fachvatn\\u011b na v\\u00fdkonn\\u00fdch po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010d\\u00edch s grafick\\u00fdmi kartami jako 3070 nebo 4090, ale z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 aby byla hrateln\\u00e1 i na star\\u0161\\u00edch stroj\\u00edch.</p>", "id": "66db5b8b-1a34-47b2-af6a-d9d308d0c872"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "87da11d9-435e-4187-904c-0ea55b1fa785"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"4zbzo\\">Majitel\\u00e9 Xbox Series S si podle v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f budou muset po\\u010dkat, ne\\u017e v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i p\\u0159ekonaj\\u00ed technick\\u00e9 v\\u00fdzvy spojen\\u00e9 s touto konzol\\u00ed. Hra by m\\u011bla dorazit ji\\u017e za\\u010d\\u00e1tkem p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00edho roku na <b>PC</b> a konzole <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"83\\"><b>PlayStation 5</b> </a>a <b>Xbox Series X/S</b>. Je ale mo\\u017en\\u00e9, \\u017ee se datum vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed na Xbox opozd\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"as3o1\\"><b>Co si o tom mysl\\u00edte vy? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f Nev\\u00e1hejte se pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 n\\u00ed\\u017ee na seznam her, kter\\u00e9 n\\u00e1s \\u010dekaj\\u00ed v z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D1rjapqeyiw&amp;t\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"epbk3\\"></p>", "id": "e47e7345-4bba-4e87-b605-d930ba44171e"}]	101	63	dune: awakening, fungcom, mmo, survival, duna, xbox series s	\N	0	1	0
