><p data-block-key=\\"1alui\\"><b>Na jak\\u00e9 nastaven\\u00ed rozehrajete Until Dawn? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. Nev\\u00e1hejte se n\\u00ed\\u017ee pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 na nejnov\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed trailer.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0LztMcaTF2g\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"33mom\\"></p>", "id": "dc1c5754-1cd6-4568-8898-857afc669297"}]	91	91	until dawn, horor, pc, hardarov poadavky, playstation	\N	0	2	0
164	Kdysi ob francouzsk spolenost Ubisoft se v poslednch letech propad do stle vt propasti a nevypad to, e by se z n mla v blzk budoucnosti dostat ven. Ale jak moc je na tom korporace patn?	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"ofgnc\\"><b>Hern\\u00ed gigant Ubisoft se v posledn\\u00edch letech propad\\u00e1 do \\u010d\\u00edm d\\u00e1l v\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed krize a zd\\u00e1 se, \\u017ee cesta ven je v nedohlednu. Ale jak v\\u00e1\\u017en\\u00e1 je situace t\\u00e9to korporace?</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"e9q19\\"><b>Ubisoft - co v\\u0161e je \\u0161patn\\u011b?</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"7hq8f\\">Kdy\\u017e jsem byl mlad\\u0161\\u00ed, francouzsk\\u00e1 hern\\u00ed spole\\u010dnost<b> Ubisoft</b> pro m\\u011b p\\u0159edstavovala symbol nezapomenuteln\\u00fdch hern\\u00edch z\\u00e1\\u017eitk\\u016f, kter\\u00e9 mistrn\\u011b kombinovaly re\\u00e1lnou historii s fantasy prvky. Dnes v\\u0161ak Ubisoft vn\\u00edm\\u00e1m jako korporaci, jej\\u00edm\\u017e c\\u00edlem je vyt\\u00e1hnout z hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f posledn\\u00ed cent. Pokud nesouhlas\\u00edme s jej\\u00edmi praktikami, \\u010dasto jsme my hr\\u00e1\\u010di obvi\\u0148ov\\u00e1ni, \\u017ee jsme ti \\u0161patn\\u00ed. Jak se ale \\u0159\\u00edk\\u00e1 <i>\\"Na ka\\u017edou svi\\u0148i se va\\u0159\\u00ed voda,\\"</i> a Ubisoft nyn\\u00ed skl\\u00edz\\u00ed, co v minulosti zasel. My se nyn\\u00ed kr\\u00e1tce pod\\u00edv\\u00e1me na to, co se t\\u00e9to spole\\u010dnosti v posledn\\u00edch letech stalo.</p>", "id": "f287c6da-25f3-43ad-85d3-105ed87c772a"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "b1258a55-bb5b-47c3-9cc2-919704300782"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"ofgnc\\">\\u0158ada ne\\u00fasp\\u011b\\u0161n\\u00fdch titul\\u016f s opakuj\\u00edc\\u00ed se \\u0161ablonou</h3><p data-block-key=\\"35t1b\\">Za\\u010dn\\u011bme n\\u011b\\u010d\\u00edm, co u\\u017e v\\u00edme v\\u0161ichni, kdo m\\u00e1me n\\u011bjak\\u00e9 ty roky na hern\\u00edm trhu za sebou. V posledn\\u00edch letech <b>Ubisoft</b> nevydal titul, kter\\u00fd by po t\\u00fddnu od sv\\u00e9ho uveden\\u00ed neupadl v zapomn\\u011bn\\u00ed, a to bez ohledu na to, zda \\u0161lo o vlajkov\\u00e9 lod\\u011b \\u010di vedlej\\u0161\\u00ed projekty. A\\u0165 u\\u017e jde o <b>Star Wars Outlaws</b>, <b>XDefiant, Assassins Creed Valhalla</b>, <b>Princ of Persia: The Lost Crown</b> nebo n\\u011bkter\\u00fd z mnoha dal\\u0161\\u00edch titul\\u016f posledn\\u00edch let, v\\u0161echny tyto hry byly bu\\u010f naprost\\u00e9 propad\\u00e1ky, nebo jen pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u011b prod\\u00e1van\\u00e9 tituly, kter\\u00e9 v\\u011bt\\u0161ina hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f po p\\u00e1r hodin\\u00e1ch hran\\u00ed odlo\\u017eila.</p><p data-block-key=\\"fcjlf\\">Pro\\u010d? Proto\\u017ee ty hry jsou nudn\\u00e9 a u\\u017e l\\u00e9ta stav\\u00ed na st\\u00e1le stejn\\u00e9 \\u0161ablon\\u011b, co\\u017e n\\u00e1s jako hr\\u00e1\\u010de za\\u010d\\u00edn\\u00e1 v\\u00e1\\u017en\\u011b unavovat a \\u0161tv\\u00e1t. Sta\\u010d\\u00ed se pod\\u00edvat na jak\\u00e9koliv video na YouTube porovn\\u00e1vaj\\u00edc\\u00ed star\\u00e9 <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/ubisoft-prinasi-novinky-ohledne-assassins-creed-shadows-zmena-modelu-season-pass-a-odlozeni-vydani\\"><b>Ubisoft</b></a> hry s t\\u011bmi nov\\u00fdmi. Gameplay se prakticky v\\u016fbec nezm\\u011bnil. To tak\\u00e9 vedlo k tomu, \\u017ee akcie spole\\u010dnosti klesly na historick\\u00e9 minimum.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B6bzlV3aHS4\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"768b1\\"></p><p data-block-key=\\"7c38p\\"><b>Ubisoft</b> m\\u00e1 tento probl\\u00e9m u\\u017e \\u0159adu let a posledn\\u00ed zm\\u011bna v celkov\\u00e9m hern\\u00edm konceptu p\\u0159i\\u0161la s vyd\\u00e1n\\u00edm Assassins Creed Origins v roce 2017, tedy p\\u0159ed sedmi lety. Repetetivnost tak sr\\u00e1\\u017e\\u00ed na kvalit\\u011b. Bohu\\u017eel to nevypad\\u00e1, \\u017ee by francouzsk\\u00fd gigant pl\\u00e1noval n\\u011bjakou dal\\u0161\\u00ed v\\u00fdraznou zm\\u011bnu. Ale to nen\\u00ed jedin\\u00fd probl\\u00e9m, kter\\u00fd tuto spole\\u010dnost tr\\u00e1p\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "736acf95-70c2-407f-8fa4-9b036276dfe7"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"ofgnc\\">Politick\\u00e1 agitace nad kvalitou titulu</h3><p data-block-key=\\"5cjcg\\"><b>Ubisoft m\\u00e1 p\\u0159ece spoustu talentovan\\u00fdch v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f, nebo snad ne?</b> No, m\\u011bl. Bohu\\u017eel mnoho z nich studio bu\\u010f opustilo, nebo byli nahrazeni nov\\u00fdmi v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i, kte\\u0159\\u00ed jsou vyb\\u00edr\\u00e1ni na z\\u00e1klad\\u011b <i>\\"politick\\u00e9 korektnosti\\"</i> ne\\u017e skute\\u010dn\\u00e9ho talentu. Zd\\u00e1 se v\\u00e1m to p\\u0159ehnan\\u00e9? K\\u00e9\\u017e by to byl vtip, ale bohu\\u017eel tomu tak nen\\u00ed. V posledn\\u00edch n\\u00e1borov\\u00fdch p\\u0159\\u00edsp\\u011bvc\\u00edch spole\\u010dnosti se explicitn\\u011b uv\\u00e1d\\u00ed, \\u017ee nov\\u00e9 zam\\u011bstnance mus\\u00ed tvo\\u0159it \\u017eeny nebo p\\u0159\\u00edslu\\u0161n\\u00edci sexu\\u00e1ln\\u00edch men\\u0161in, co\\u017e se prom\\u00edt\\u00e1 i do samotn\\u00e9ho obsahu her. Sp\\u00ed\\u0161e ne\\u017e zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00ed na kvalitu her a jejich p\\u0159\\u00edb\\u011bh se <b>Ubisoft</b> o\\u010dividn\\u011b soust\\u0159ed\\u00ed na spl\\u0148ov\\u00e1n\\u00ed ur\\u010dit\\u00fdch politick\\u00fdch standard\\u016f.</p><p data-block-key=\\"fpj46\\">Tato skute\\u010dnost vedla k tomu, \\u017ee nap\\u0159\\u00edklad hra <b>Assassins Creed: Shadows</b> \\u010del\\u00ed siln\\u00e9 kritice a bojkotu zejm\\u00e9na ze strany japonsk\\u00fdch hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, a dokonce i japonsk\\u00e9ho sen\\u00e1tu. Pro\\u010d? Proto\\u017ee se v n\\u00ed odr\\u00e1\\u017eej\\u00ed pr\\u00e1v\\u011b tyto politicky motivovan\\u00e9 prvky, kter\\u00e9 v o\\u010d\\u00edch mnoha hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f naru\\u0161uj\\u00ed autenticitu p\\u0159\\u00edb\\u011bhu a celkov\\u00fd z\\u00e1\\u017eitek.</p><p data-block-key=\\"gpo1\\"><br/>Cel\\u00fd probl\\u00e9m by nebyl tak vyhrocen\\u00fd, kdyby tato <i>\\"politick\\u00e1 agitace\\"</i> nebyla do her n\\u00e1siln\\u011b tla\\u010dena a hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm vnucov\\u00e1na. V\\u011bt\\u0161in\\u011b z n\\u00e1s je toti\\u017e \\u00fapln\\u011b jedno, jak\\u00e9 pohlav\\u00ed nebo sexu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed orientaci m\\u00e1 hlavn\\u00ed nebo vedlej\\u0161\\u00ed postava, pokud je dob\\u0159e napsan\\u00e1 a m\\u00e1 siln\\u00fd charakter. My hr\\u00e1\\u010di chceme postavy, kter\\u00e9 maj\\u00ed hloubku a jsou zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9, a ne ty, kter\\u00e9 p\\u016fsob\\u00ed, jako by byly vytvo\\u0159en\\u00e9 jen proto, aby splnily kv\\u00f3ty. Bohu\\u017eel to nen\\u00ed jen o hr\\u00e1ch, za t\\u011bmito rozhodnut\\u00edmi stoj\\u00ed i organizace jako <b>Sweet Baby</b> a <b>Gamer Gate</b>, kter\\u00e9 tla\\u010d\\u00ed na korporace, aby se zam\\u011b\\u0159ovaly na<i> politicky spr\\u00e1vn\\u00e9</i> prvky sp\\u00ed\\u0161e ne\\u017e na kvalitn\\u00ed hern\\u00ed obsah. Tento trend se ale st\\u00e1le v\\u00edce ukazuje jako nep\\u0159ijateln\\u00fd pro \\u0161ir\\u0161\\u00ed hern\\u00ed komunitu.</p>", "id": "0f158c21-c19c-439a-a75e-cfcf6b75356f"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "4e3e142c-ef16-442e-a99f-29a1d0e1264f"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"ofgnc\\">Je to vina hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f!</h3><p data-block-key=\\"78vue\\">Poj\\u010fme se te\\u010f pod\\u00edvat na n\\u011bco, co v\\u00e1s mo\\u017en\\u00e1 pobav\\u00ed. Ned\\u00e1vno se na webu <b>9Gag</b> objevila zpr\\u00e1va, \\u017ee \\u0161\\u00e9f Ubisoftu <b>Yves Guillemot</b> obvi\\u0148uje hr\\u00e1\\u010de z ne\\u00fasp\\u011bchu spole\\u010dnosti. Podle jeho slov hr\\u00e1\\u010di vy\\u017eaduj\\u00ed ne\\u010dekan\\u00e9 z\\u00e1\\u017eitky a dokonale vylad\\u011bn\\u00e9 hry hned p\\u0159i vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed, a pr\\u00fd u\\u017e nesta\\u010d\\u00ed ani tvorba kvalitn\\u00edch her.</p><p data-block-key=\\"dagpi\\"><br/>Ano, \\u010dtete spr\\u00e1vn\\u011b. Podle v\\u00fdkonn\\u00e9ho \\u0159editele Ubisoftu je za \\u0161patn\\u00fd stav spole\\u010dnosti zodpov\\u011bdn\\u00e1 p\\u0159ehnan\\u00e1 n\\u00e1ro\\u010dnost a vyb\\u00edravost samotn\\u00fdch hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f. Up\\u0159\\u00edmn\\u011b, tohle je sm\\u011b\\u0161n\\u00e1 v\\u00fdmluva. Kdy\\u017e se pod\\u00edv\\u00e1me na \\u00fasp\\u011b\\u0161n\\u00e9 hern\\u00ed tituly z tohoto roku, zjist\\u00edme, \\u017ee \\u017e\\u00e1dn\\u00e1 z nich nen\\u00ed revolu\\u010dn\\u00ed, co se gameplaye t\\u00fd\\u010de. Rozd\\u00edl je v tom, \\u017ee tyto hry jsou z\\u00e1bavn\\u00e9 a sv\\u00fdm z\\u00e1kazn\\u00edk\\u016fm za jejich pen\\u00edze opravdu poskytuj\\u00ed to, co slibuj\\u00ed. Na rozd\\u00edl od posledn\\u00edch her od Ubisoftu se nesna\\u017e\\u00ed vyt\\u00e1hnout hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm posledn\\u00ed korunu.</p>", "id": "3116119c-aa16-4e83-80cc-55f73ce5a905"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"ofgnc\\">Mo\\u017en\\u00fd odkup</h3><p data-block-key=\\"1395e\\">U\\u017e v roce 2022 to vypadalo, \\u017ee se <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/akcie-ubisoftu-opet-vyrazne-klesly-nejistota-roste\\"><b>Ubisoft</b></a> ocitne ve sp\\u00e1rech \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00e9ho giganta <b>Tencent</b>, ale nakonec v\\u0161e skon\\u010dilo jen nav\\u00fd\\u0161en\\u00edm investic do spole\\u010dnosti. O dva roky pozd\\u011bji se v\\u0161ak mo\\u017enost odkupu firmy jev\\u00ed jako st\\u00e1le re\\u00e1ln\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed, zejm\\u00e9na kv\\u016fli nespokojenosti akcion\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f, kte\\u0159\\u00ed po prudk\\u00e9m poklesu hodnoty akci\\u00ed volaj\\u00ed po zm\\u011bn\\u011b veden\\u00ed. Jednou z navrhovan\\u00fdch zm\\u011bn je pr\\u00e1v\\u011b odkup Ubisoftu do soukrom\\u00e9ho vlastnictv\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"7q5ch\\">Zat\\u00edm jde o jednu z mo\\u017enost\\u00ed, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e na stole je je\\u0161t\\u011b n\\u011bkolik dal\\u0161\\u00edch alternativ, ale pokud bude spole\\u010dnost pokra\\u010dovat ve sv\\u00e9 sou\\u010dasn\\u00e9 strategii, m\\u016f\\u017ee se tento odkup uk\\u00e1zat jako jedin\\u00e9 mo\\u017en\\u00e9 \\u0159e\\u0161en\\u00ed. Veden\\u00ed si mus\\u00ed uv\\u011bdomit, \\u017ee jejich aktu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed kroky firmu sp\\u00ed\\u0161e po\\u0161kozuj\\u00ed, a bude nutn\\u00e9 zm\\u011bnit p\\u0159\\u00edstup k v\\u00fdvoji her.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZsFFpY2cOo8\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"au79a\\"></p>", "id": "fe2a534e-bcb4-4557-a4db-74e3a41eb529"}]	162	125	ubisoft, problmy, krize, videohry, budoucnost	\N	0	4	0
178	Ped pr dny Microsoft uspodal prezentaci pro sv partnery, kde pedstavil plny pro hre na pt rok. Pro vs jsme tak vybrali ty nejzajmavj novinky.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yubz2\\"><b>Ned\\u00e1vno spole\\u010dnost Microsoft zorganizovala men\\u0161\\u00ed setk\\u00e1n\\u00ed pro sv\\u00e9 partnery, kde prezentovala nadch\\u00e1zej\\u00edc\\u00ed novinky pro hr\\u00e1\\u010de na p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00ed rok. Vyfiltrovali jsme tak ty nejzaj\\u00edmav\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed tituly pro v\\u00e1s.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"f8o9n\\"><b>Zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 hry z Xbox Partner Preview 2024</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"b1c99\\">P\\u0159esto\\u017ee spole\\u010dnost <b>Microsoft</b> disponuje v r\\u00e1mci sv\\u00e9 hern\\u00ed divize Xbox mnoha vlastn\\u00edmi studii, spolupracuje tak\\u00e9 s \\u0159adou extern\\u00edch partner\\u016f na v\\u00fdvoji nov\\u00fdch titul\\u016f pro jejich platformu. Pr\\u00e1v\\u011b proto zorganizovala prezentaci <b>Xbox Partner Preview 2024</b>, kde tito partne\\u0159i p\\u0159edstavili projekty, na kter\\u00fdch pracuj\\u00ed pro nadch\\u00e1zej\\u00edc\\u00ed rok. Vybral jsem tak pro v\\u00e1s ty nejlep\\u0161\\u00ed a nejzaj\\u00edmav\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed hry, kter\\u00e9 byly na t\\u00e9to akci uk\\u00e1z\\u00e1ny.</p>", "id": "2c380878-1868-49aa-8ead-55d6f15e62b0"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "620d194f-6c33-4c13-b028-74ef140ecc09"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"yubz2\\">Cronos: The New Dawn</h3><p data-block-key=\\"818ge\\">S p\\u0159\\u00edchodem \\u0159\\u00edjna je \\u010das na n\\u011bco, co v\\u00e1m nahod\\u00ed hus\\u00ed k\\u016f\\u017ei. <b>Cronos: The New Dawn</b> je nejnov\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed survival horor od studia Bloober Team S.A., kter\\u00e9 ned\\u00e1vno skl\\u00edzelo \\u00fasp\\u011bchy s remakem <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/konami-odhaluje-casy-vydani-silent-hill-2-remake-prvni-recenze-jiz-zverejneny\\"><b>Silent Hill 2</b></a>. Titul n\\u00e1s zavede do postapokalyptick\\u00e9 budoucnosti Evropy, kde se denn\\u011b, ka\\u017edou hodinu, ka\\u017edou sekundu mus\\u00edme rv\\u00e1t o p\\u0159e\\u017eit\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"5aiao\\">V t\\u00e9to nehostinn\\u00e9 budoucnosti se ujmeme role sb\\u011bratele du\\u0161\\u00ed, kter\\u00fd m\\u00e1 za \\u00fakol naj\\u00edt specifick\\u00e9 osoby, aby je zachr\\u00e1nil p\\u0159ed nadch\\u00e1zej\\u00edc\\u00ed katastrofou. Kdo v\\u0161echno se ocitne na na\\u0161em seznamu? Odpov\\u011b\\u010f p\\u0159ijde a\\u017e p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00ed rok. P\\u0159esn\\u00fd datum vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed sice z\\u016fst\\u00e1v\\u00e1 zahalen tajemstv\\u00edm, ale mohu prozradit, \\u017ee atmosf\\u00e9ra hry je dosud naprosto pohlcuj\\u00edc\\u00ed. No pod\\u00edvejte se sami.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sp5X_7OGoBA\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"cpt9m\\"></p>", "id": "fc683553-0fb1-4096-b3b7-e936fd34267c"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"yubz2\\">MOUSE: P.I. For Hire</h3><p data-block-key=\\"1607q\\">Mus\\u00edm se v\\u00e1m p\\u0159iznat, \\u017ee tento titul sleduji ji\\u017e n\\u011bjakou dobu a nedo\\u010dkav\\u011b o\\u010dek\\u00e1v\\u00e1m jeho vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed. Jedn\\u00e1 se o indie ak\\u010dn\\u00ed FPS st\\u0159\\u00edle\\u010dku od studia <b>Fumi Games</b>, kter\\u00e1 sv\\u00fdm designem evokuje ran\\u00e9 Disneyho animace. V roli soukrom\\u00e9ho detektiva Jacka Peppera, kter\\u00fd se neboj\\u00ed prol\\u00edt tuny krve a olova za \\u00fa\\u010delem z\\u00edsk\\u00e1n\\u00ed d\\u016fkaz\\u016f k vy\\u0159e\\u0161en\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edpad\\u016f, n\\u00e1s s nejvy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed pravd\\u011bpodobnost\\u00ed \\u010dek\\u00e1 \\u0161\\u00edlen\\u00fd ak\\u010dn\\u00ed z\\u00e1\\u017eitek s n\\u00e1dechem detektivn\\u00ed pr\\u00e1ce.</p><p data-block-key=\\"bvrcl\\">P\\u0159\\u00edb\\u011bh hry, kter\\u00fd napodobuje star\\u00e9 noirov\\u00e9 detektivky, je zaj\\u00edmav\\u011b koncipov\\u00e1n. V n\\u011bkter\\u00fdch aspektech je gameplay podobn\\u00fd slavn\\u00e9 hern\\u00ed s\\u00e9rii <b>Bioshock</b>, co\\u017e h\\u0159e dod\\u00e1v\\u00e1 na charakteru. Velmi se t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edm na to, jak se v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016fm poda\\u0159\\u00ed tento unik\\u00e1tn\\u00ed hern\\u00ed z\\u00e1\\u017eitek zrealizovat v p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00edm roce, i kdy\\u017e p\\u0159esn\\u00e9 datum vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed zat\\u00edm z\\u016fst\\u00e1v\\u00e1 nezn\\u00e1m\\u00e9.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yN7RNcKMA_g\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"403at\\"></p>", "id": "6cc15152-2c91-45a0-8bdd-5d368de46e24"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "42e8d6da-bcb2-4d4d-a5da-ea36fc6ab407"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"yubz2\\"><b>Subnautica 2</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"3vc6v\\">Fanou\\u0161ci sandbox survival s\\u00e9rie <b>Subnautica</b> dlouh\\u00e1 l\\u00e9ta vyhl\\u00ed\\u017eeli pokra\\u010dov\\u00e1n\\u00ed, kter\\u00e9 bylo kone\\u010dn\\u011b ozn\\u00e1meno na ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e9 prezentaci. Subnautica 2 n\\u00e1s op\\u011bt zavede do podvodn\\u00edho sv\\u011bta nezn\\u00e1m\\u00e9 planety, kde se budeme v\\u011bnovat studiu, pr\\u016fzkumu a stav\\u011bn\\u00ed r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch p\\u0159\\u00edbytk\\u016f, n\\u00e1stroj\\u016f a vozidel.</p><p data-block-key=\\"ed3n4\\">Hra vyjde p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00ed rok v p\\u0159edb\\u011b\\u017en\\u00e9m p\\u0159\\u00edstupu, co\\u017e m\\u016f\\u017ee n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 nov\\u00e9 hr\\u00e1\\u010de odradit. Nicm\\u00e9n\\u011b my, zku\\u0161en\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010di, v\\u00edme, \\u017ee v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i \\u0161li stejnou cestou ji\\u017e u prvn\\u00edho d\\u00edlu a Below Zero. Jsem opravdu zv\\u011bdav, co v\\u0161e nov\\u00e9 pokra\\u010dov\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159inese jak fanou\\u0161k\\u016fm, tak nov\\u00e1\\u010dk\\u016fm t\\u00e9to s\\u00e9rie.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MDO_VxUSOGI\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"61jbp\\"></p>", "id": "5ffcff61-7b03-4733-9d9d-134a6f5c3c29"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"yubz2\\">WUCHANG: Fallen Feathers</h3><p data-block-key=\\"31hvr\\">Jako dal\\u0161\\u00ed v\\u00fdznamn\\u00fd titul zm\\u00edn\\u00edm ne\\u010dekanou souls-like hru, kterou vyd\\u00e1v\\u00e1 studio 505 Games, zn\\u00e1m\\u00e9 sv\\u00fdmi hrami Ghostrunner 1 a 2 \\u010di Crime Boss: Rockay City. Hra, nazvan\\u00e1 <b>WUCHANG: Fallen Feathers</b>, je prvn\\u00edm projektem nov\\u011b vznikl\\u00e9ho \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00e9ho studia Leenzee. D\\u011bj hry n\\u00e1s zavede do \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00e9 zem\\u011b Shu b\\u011bhem temn\\u00e9ho obdob\\u00ed pozdn\\u00ed dynastie Ming, kde se hr\\u00e1\\u010di v\\u017eij\\u00ed do role Wuchang, zku\\u0161en\\u00e9 pir\\u00e1tsk\\u00e9 bojovnice trp\\u00edc\\u00ed amnesi\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"60jre\\">Krom\\u011b boje s vlastn\\u00edmi vzpom\\u00ednkami mus\\u00ed Wuchang \\u010delit abilit\\u011b zvan\\u00e9 Feathering, kter\\u00e1 j\\u00ed prop\\u016fj\\u010duje schopnost ukr\\u00e1st magick\\u00e9 s\\u00edly sv\\u00fdch nep\\u0159\\u00e1tel a pou\\u017e\\u00edt je proti nim. \\u010cek\\u00e1 ji dlouh\\u00e1 cesta pln\\u00e1 boj\\u016f s nadp\\u0159irozen\\u00fdmi silami a monstry z \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00e9 mytologie. V\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i slibuj\\u00ed bohat\\u00fd p\\u0159\\u00edb\\u011bh, dynamick\\u00fd soubojov\\u00fd syst\\u00e9m, dechberouc\\u00ed vizu\\u00e1l a nezapomenuteln\\u00e9 dobrodru\\u017estv\\u00ed v chaotick\\u00e9m a smrteln\\u00e9m sv\\u011bt\\u011b.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HPqHQ4ZNI_Q\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"4b7ij\\"></p>", "id": "4a620090-9a30-40ef-8dd7-bef881b32210"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "3faa0b79-3716-4563-bf21-4a543a6a0911"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"yubz2\\">\\u010cestn\\u00e9 zm\\u00ednky</h3><p data-block-key=\\"bhhfv\\">Na prezentaci se samoz\\u0159ejm\\u011b p\\u0159edstavily i dal\\u0161\\u00ed zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 hry, ale vzhledem k \\u010dasov\\u00e9 n\\u00e1ro\\u010dnosti by bylo nemo\\u017en\\u00e9 pokr\\u00fdt je v\\u0161echny v jednom \\u010dl\\u00e1nku. Proto jsem se rozhodl zm\\u00ednit je zat\\u00edm jen okrajov\\u011b a s nejvy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed pravd\\u011bpodobnost\\u00ed se k nim vr\\u00e1t\\u00edm v budoucnu.</p><p data-block-key=\\"hq6m\\">Jedn\\u00edm z t\\u011bchto titul\\u016f je <b>Mistfall Hunter</b>, ak\\u010dn\\u00ed PvPvE RPG z pohledu t\\u0159et\\u00ed osoby. Hra n\\u00e1s zavede do temn\\u00e9ho fantasy sv\\u011bta pln\\u00e9ho monster, kde mus\\u00edte b\\u00fdt neust\\u00e1le na pozoru nejen p\\u0159ed nestv\\u016frami, ale i p\\u0159ed ostatn\\u00edmi hr\\u00e1\\u010di. P\\u0159esn\\u00e9 datum vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed zat\\u00edm nen\\u00ed zn\\u00e1m\\u00e9.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MnZtFtzMctY\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"epp18\\"><b>The Legend of Baboo</b> je roztomil\\u00e1 ak\\u010dn\\u00ed adventura, kter\\u00e1 n\\u00e1s sezn\\u00e1m\\u00ed s p\\u0159\\u00edb\\u011bhem mlad\\u00e9ho chlapce jm\\u00e9nem Sepehr a jeho v\\u011brn\\u00e9ho psa Baboo. Hra n\\u00e1s zavede do barevn\\u00e9ho a magick\\u00e9ho sv\\u011bta, kde nebudeme \\u010delit jen souboj\\u016fm s nep\\u0159\\u00e1teli, ale tak\\u00e9 budeme muset vy\\u0159e\\u0161it n\\u011bkolik zapeklit\\u00fdch h\\u00e1danek. Datum vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed zat\\u00edm nebylo ozn\\u00e1meno.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-zVC2Jg9xM\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"919v5\\">Pro fanou\\u0161ky studia <b>Remedy</b> a p\\u0159edev\\u0161\\u00edm hry <b>Control</b> by mohla b\\u00fdt zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e1 nov\\u00e1 hra FBC: Firebreak. Ve h\\u0159e se vr\\u00e1t\\u00edme zp\\u011bt do zn\\u00e1m\\u00e9ho institutu z Control. Jedn\\u00e1 se o koopera\\u010dn\\u00ed FPS st\\u0159\\u00edle\