165	Nedvn studie, kter se zamila na vce ne tisc hr, odhalila zajmav vsledky. League of Legends m nejinteligentnj hrskou zkladnu.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"836ww\\"><b>Studie, kter\\u00e1 se zam\\u011b\\u0159ila na inteligenci hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch her, odhalila, \\u017ee nejchyt\\u0159ej\\u0161\\u00ed z\\u00e1kladnu maj\\u00ed fanou\\u0161ci League of Legends.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"6ge5g\\"><b>League of Legends m\\u00e1 nejchyt\\u0159ej\\u0161\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010dskou z\\u00e1kladnu?</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"bouov\\">Ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e1 studie spole\\u010dnosti <b>WhichBingo</b>, podpo\\u0159en\\u00e1 t\\u00fdmem psycholog\\u016f, zjistila, \\u017ee hr\\u00e1\\u010di <b>League of Legends</b> jsou mezi hr\\u00e1\\u010dsk\\u00fdmi komunitami t\\u011bmi s nejvy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00edm IQ. A to nen\\u00ed v\\u0161e. V\\u00fdsledky p\\u0159inesly \\u0159adu z\\u00e1bavn\\u00fdch post\\u0159eh\\u016f. </p><p data-block-key=\\"3su4n\\">V\\u00fdzkum prok\\u00e1zal, \\u017ee pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u00e9 IQ hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f League of Legends dosahuje velmi impozantn\\u00edch <b>120,4 bod\\u016f</b>, co\\u017e je nejv\\u00edce mezi v\\u0161emi sledovan\\u00fdmi hrami. Samoz\\u0159ejm\\u011b kdy\\u017e se zamysl\\u00edme nad slo\\u017eitost\\u00ed hry, nen\\u00ed p\\u0159ekvapen\\u00edm, \\u017ee hr\\u00e1\\u010di mus\\u00ed m\\u00edt dob\\u0159e nabrou\\u0161en\\u00e9 ment\\u00e1ln\\u00ed schopnosti, aby v n\\u00ed excelovali.</p><p data-block-key=\\"37tnr\\">Slo\\u017eit\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed tituly, jako je <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/black-myth-wukong-slavi-velky-financni-uspech\\"><b>Black Myth: Wukong</b></a> s pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u00fdm IQ <b>119,8</b>, jasn\\u011b p\\u0159itahuj\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010de s vy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00edmi kognitivn\\u00edmi schopnostmi. Hr\\u00e1\\u010di titul\\u016f <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/larian-studios-vydalo-patch-7-pro-baldurs-gate-3\\"><b>Baldur\\u2019s Gate 3</b></a>, <b>Counter-Strike</b> a <b>Elden Ring</b> se rovn\\u011b\\u017e um\\u00edstili vysoko.</p><p data-block-key=\\"850k4\\">Na opa\\u010dn\\u00e9m konci \\u017eeb\\u0159\\u00ed\\u010dku se ocitly hry jako <b>FC 24</b> a <b>Rocket League</b>, jejich\\u017e hr\\u00e1\\u010di vykazuj\\u00ed pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u00e9 IQ kolem <b>90 bod\\u016f</b>. Nejh\\u016f\\u0159e tak dopadli hr\\u00e1\\u010di fotbalov\\u00fdch simul\\u00e1tor\\u016f.</p>", "id": "0a6439d0-632b-49af-aa59-d0a324dabe4b"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "b1d73c99-00ca-4e67-9963-21c86e2cc251"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"836ww\\">\\u010c\\u00edm slo\\u017eit\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed hra, t\\u00edm chyt\\u0159ej\\u0161\\u00ed je jej\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010dsk\\u00e1 z\\u00e1kladna. Uprost\\u0159ed \\u017eeb\\u0159\\u00ed\\u010dku najdeme hry jako <b>Battlefield 2042, Destiny 2 a</b> <b>Escape from Tarkov</b>, kde se pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u00e9 IQ pohybuje okolo <b>105 bod\\u016f</b>. Zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 v\\u0161ak je, \\u017ee hr\\u00e1\\u010di <b>Call of Duty: Warzone</b> a <b>Modern Warfare 3</b> se um\\u00edstili na ni\\u017e\\u0161\\u00edch p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u010dk\\u00e1ch, konkr\\u00e9tn\\u011b s pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u00fdm IQ <b>95,3</b>. Celou tabulku naleznete pod p\\u0159ilo\\u017een\\u00fdm odkazem <a href=\\"https://www.whichbingo.co.uk/news/which-gamers-are-the-smartest/\\"><b>ZDE</b></a>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"8p7mm\\"><b>Z pohledu na\\u0161\\u00ed redakce je tento pr\\u016fzkum sice \\u00fasm\\u011bvn\\u00fd, ale z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 velmi zaj\\u00edmav\\u00fd. Do jak\\u00e9 kategorie hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f se \\u0159ad\\u00edte vy? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt n\\u00ed\\u017ee do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. A nev\\u00e1hejte se pod\\u00edvat na na\\u0161e nejnov\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed video n\\u00ed\\u017ee.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxjZ13qz7Ys\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"7pa2\\"