137	Na sv kadoron konferenci Unite 2024 oznmila spolenost Unity, e jej nejnovj a nejvkonnj verze, Unity 6, bude sputna celosvtov v jnu.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"i56z4\\"><b>Unity 6 p\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016fm vylep\\u0161en\\u00e9 grafick\\u00e9 mo\\u017enosti, zjednodu\\u0161en\\u00fd v\\u00fdvoj multiplayerov\\u00fdch her a robustn\\u00ed n\\u00e1stroje pro optimalizaci her pro webov\\u00e9 prohl\\u00ed\\u017ee\\u010de.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"e2356\\"><b>Unity 6 ji\\u017e v z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"8b47u\\">Na konferenci <b>Unite 2024</b> konan\\u00e9 v Barcelon\\u011b dnes spole\\u010dnost <b>Unity</b> ozn\\u00e1mila, \\u017ee dlouho o\\u010dek\\u00e1van\\u00e1 verze jejich hern\\u00edho enginu <b>Unity 6</b> bude ofici\\u00e1ln\\u011b spu\\u0161t\\u011bna 17. \\u0159\\u00edjna 2024.</p><p data-block-key=\\"db51j\\">Mezi prvn\\u00edmi v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i, kte\\u0159\\u00ed se pustili do pr\\u00e1ce s Unity 6, je studio <b>10 Chambers,</b> zn\\u00e1m\\u00e9 d\\u00edky h\\u0159e <b>GTFO</b>. Na konferenci Unite p\\u0159edvedli prost\\u0159ed\\u00ed ze sv\\u00e9 p\\u0159ipravovan\\u00e9 hry Den of Wolves, kter\\u00e9 vyu\\u017e\\u00edv\\u00e1 nejmodern\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed grafick\\u00e9 technologie, je\\u017e Unity 6 nab\\u00edz\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "b3b7616f-fd05-47fd-8ded-2a6d0e781cca"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "50dbe9e6-ebc1-471b-b095-dd1d2a00880f"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"i56z4\\">Spole\\u010dnost Unity z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 ozn\\u00e1mila, \\u017ee prvn\\u00ed aktualizace Unity 6.1 bude k dispozici u\\u017e v dubnu p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00edho roku. Aktualizace p\\u0159inese podporu pro v\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed obrazovky, Deferred+ rendering v GPU Resident Drawer a nov\\u00e9 build c\\u00edle a profily, kter\\u00e9 poskytnou v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016fm dal\\u0161\\u00ed mo\\u017enosti p\\u0159i tvorb\\u011b jejich projekt\\u016f.</p><p data-block-key=\\"f3uvi\\">B\\u011bhem konference Unite 2024 byly p\\u0159edstaveny i dal\\u0161\\u00ed zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 novinky. Pat\\u0159\\u00ed mezi n\\u011b intern\\u00ed techdemo s n\\u00e1zvem <b>Time Ghost</b>, kter\\u00fd ukazuje pln\\u00fd potenci\\u00e1l Unity 6, a optimalizovan\\u00e1 verze projektu Fantasy Kingdom pro mobiln\\u00ed za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"fk3de\\"><b>Na techdemo Time Ghost se m\\u016f\\u017eete pod\\u00edvat n\\u00ed\\u017ee. Co \\u0159\\u00edk\\u00e1te na novou verzi tohoto enginu? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1JIK5W3DRU\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"3t57f\\"></p>", "id": "8a8ffe2d-0556-4fe7-9bda-f697969798c6"}]	22	103	unity 6, unity, techdemo, engine	\N	0	3	0
61	Na letonm ronku akce Gamescom se krom velkch titul ukzala i ada tch mench, kter zaujmou jen urit publikum hr. A jednm z tchto titul byla i len kooperativn survival mltika King of Meat. Ale co se vechno skrv za tmto nzv	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"l54rg\\"><b>Na leto\\u0161n\\u00edm ro\\u010dn\\u00edku akce Gamescom se krom\\u011b velk\\u00fdch titul\\u016f uk\\u00e1zala i \\u0159ada t\\u011bch men\\u0161\\u00edch. A jedn\\u00edm z t\\u011bchto titul\\u016f byla i \\u0161\\u00edlen\\u00e1 kooperativn\\u00ed survival ml\\u00e1ti\\u010dka King of Meat. Ale co se v\\u0161e skr\\u00fdv\\u00e1 za t\\u00edmto vizu\\u00e1lem \\u0161\\u00edlenstv\\u00ed.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"bauho\\"><b>Co je King of Meat?</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"7d6o0\\">Leto\\u0161n\\u00ed ro\\u010dn\\u00edk akce <b>Gamescom</b> sice nenab\\u00eddl moc zaj\\u00edmav\\u00fdch titul\\u016f pro v\\u011bt\\u0161inu hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, ale i tak jsem se do\\u010dkali po\\u0159\\u00e1dn\\u00fdch <b>gameplay z\\u00e1b\\u011br\\u016f z o\\u010dek\\u00e1van\\u00fdch her</b>, tak i p\\u00e1r <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"56\\"><b>p\\u0159ekvapiv\\u00fdch ozn\\u00e1men\\u00ed</b></a>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"3dipc\\">A i kdy\\u017e se n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 tituly od indie studi\\u00ed zam\\u011b\\u0159uj\\u00ed na r\\u016fznorod\\u00e9 mal\\u00e9 hern\\u00ed komunity, v p\\u0159\\u00edpad\\u011b <b>King of Meat</b> je jeho obsah zam\\u011b\\u0159en na v\\u00edce hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, ne\\u017e si mysl\\u00edte. Na jej\\u00ed tvorb\\u011b sice pracuje mal\\u00e9 americk\\u00e9 indie studio <b>Glowmade</b>, ale studio samotn\\u00e9 je pod z\\u00e1\\u0161titou Amazon Games. Ale te\\u010f bez zbyte\\u010dn\\u00e9ho ot\\u00e1len\\u00ed se na hru lehce pod\\u00edv\\u00e1me.</p>", "id": "f520adce-97af-4102-9535-ad39310c0e48"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "f77dcd23-782b-4b97-8ba0-1785d72fc4f2"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"l54rg\\"><b>O co vlastn\\u011b jde?</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"9532c\\">Poj\\u010fme tedy na z\\u00e1kladn\\u00ed informace o t\\u00e9to h\\u0159e. <b>King of Meat</b> je prim\\u00e1rn\\u011b kooperativn\\u00ed survival ml\\u00e1ti\\u010dka, kde vy a dal\\u0161\\u00ed t\\u0159i kamar\\u00e1di se po hlav\\u011b vrhnete do \\u0161\\u00edlen\\u00fdch dungeon\\u016f vytvo\\u0159en\\u00fdch bu\\u010f v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i, nebo hr\\u00e1\\u010di samotn\\u00fdmi.</p><p data-block-key=\\"bm6d2\\">V ka\\u017ed\\u00e9m z t\\u011bchto dungeon\\u016f se nach\\u00e1zej\\u00ed r\\u016fzn\\u00e9 smrt\\u00edc\\u00ed pasti, nep\\u0159\\u00e1tel\\u00e9, skryt\\u00e9 st\\u011bny a tak\\u00e9 hromada zlata a drahokam\\u016f. Ale nebojte, hra v\\u00e1s hned nehod\\u00ed do multiplayeru k ostatn\\u00edm hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm do \\u0161\\u00edlen\\u00fdch nebezpe\\u010dn\\u00fdch dungeon\\u016f, ale nejd\\u0159\\u00edve v\\u00e1s provede p\\u0159\\u00edv\\u011btivou singleplayerovou kampan\\u00ed, kde se nau\\u010d\\u00edte v\\u0161echny z\\u00e1klady hry.</p>", "id": "1f52b230-cb54-40ef-b6a4-e15b633a0078"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"l54rg\\"><b>Dv\\u011b \\u010d\\u00e1sti pro ka\\u017ed\\u00e9ho?</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"au10c\\">Jak jste ji\\u017e pochopili, samotn\\u00fd titul bude m\\u00edt celkem 2 odd\\u011blen\\u00e9 \\u010d\\u00e1sti. Prvn\\u00ed z nich je <b>proch\\u00e1zen\\u00ed samotn\\u00fdch dungeon\\u016f</b> s ostatn\\u00edmi hr\\u00e1\\u010di a druh\\u00e1 pak bude i vytv\\u00e1\\u0159en\\u00ed samotn\\u00fdch dungeon\\u016f pro ostatn\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010de. A tato tvorba se bude m\\u011b\\u0159it podle 3 krit\\u00e9ri\\u00ed: mno\\u017estv\\u00ed samotn\\u00fdch m\\u00edstnost\\u00ed, jejich logi\\u010dnost a komplexnost. D\\u00edky tomu mohou m\\u00edt kreativn\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010di p\\u0159ehled o tom, jak n\\u00e1ro\\u010dn\\u00e1 jejich mapa bude pro ostatn\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "f76b90af-f915-4ea9-96af-f86e6d899b35"}, {"type": "adve