139	I kdy to nen Days Gone 2, zd se, e franza by mohla najt cestu na PlayStation 5. Podle nedvnch spekulac by remaster populrn hry Days Gone mohl bt brzy oznmen	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"zseb0\\"><b>Zv\\u011bsti o Days Gone pro PlayStation 5 z\\u00edsk\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed na s\\u00edle. P\\u0159esto\\u017ee ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00ed potvrzen\\u00ed zat\\u00edm chyb\\u00ed, spekulace nazna\\u010duj\\u00ed, \\u017ee tato popul\\u00e1rn\\u00ed postapokalyptick\\u00e1 hra by se mohla brzy do\\u010dkat nov\\u00e9 verze na aktu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed generaci konzol\\u00ed. </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"8igka\\"><b>Days Gone remaster</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"18sks\\">P\\u0159\\u00e1li byste si Days Gone remaster? A\\u010dkoliv zat\\u00edm nedo\\u0161lo k ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00edmu ozn\\u00e1men\\u00ed, zv\\u011bsti za\\u010daly nab\\u00edrat na s\\u00edle po ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e9m n\\u00e1znaku hern\\u00edho novin\\u00e1\\u0159e Jordana Middlera, kter\\u00fd nazna\\u010dil, \\u017ee tento titul by mohl b\\u00fdt jedn\\u00edm z p\\u0159ekvapen\\u00ed nadch\\u00e1zej\\u00edc\\u00ed akce <b>State of Play</b> od <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/playstation-5-prekonal-61-milionu-prodanych-kusu-xbox-zas-stavi-na-rustu-predplatneho\\"><b>PlayStation</b></a>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"cebp3\\">Jordan Middler rozpoutal toti\\u017e vlnu spekulac\\u00ed prost\\u0159ednictv\\u00edm sv\\u00e9ho p\\u0159\\u00edsp\\u011bvku na Twitteru. Reagoval na debaty ohledn\\u011b \\u00fadajn\\u00e9ho remasteru <b>Horizon Zero Dawn</b>. Middlerov\\u00fdm koment\\u00e1\\u0159em, \\u017ee pokud n\\u011bkoho roz\\u010d\\u00edlilo, \\u017ee jeho postava byla pou\\u017eita v <b>Astro Bot</b>, <i>tak z remasteru Days Gone ztrat\\u00ed rozum,</i> je\\u0161t\\u011b v\\u00edce p\\u0159idal olej do ohn\\u011b. N\\u00e1znak o Days Gone remasteru okam\\u017eit\\u011b vyvolal bou\\u0159liv\\u00e9 diskuse mezi fanou\\u0161ky i kritiky.</p><p data-block-key=\\"b7vri\\">Ot\\u00e1zkou v\\u0161ak z