142	Spolenost Sony nedvno odhalila novinku v podob PlayStation 5 Pro, kter pin vylepen v polovin generace. Microsoft vak vsadil na pln jin pstup a hodl hre ohromit zcela novou generac hardwaru.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"9bdh8\\"><b>M\\u00edsto o\\u010dek\\u00e1van\\u00e9ho mezigenera\\u010dn\\u00edho vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed, jak\\u00e9 p\\u0159inesl Xbox One X, Microsoft soust\\u0159ed\\u00ed ve\\u0161kerou svou energii na p\\u0159\\u00edpravu nov\\u00e9 konzole, kter\\u00e1 m\\u00e1 nab\\u00eddnout nejv\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed technologick\\u00fd pokrok v historii hern\\u00edho pr\\u016fmyslu.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"1f54p\\"><b>Microsoft jde jinou cestou ne\\u017e Sony</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"3agfi\\">Spole\\u010dnost Sony postupuje podle ov\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00e9ho sc\\u00e9n\\u00e1\\u0159e a roz\\u0161i\\u0159uje svou nab\\u00eddku o vylep\\u0161enou<a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/playstation-5-pro-se-v-cesku-dostava-pres-zajimavou-cenovou-uroven\\"> <b>PlayStation 5 Pro</b></a>, <b>Microsoft</b> se rozhodl vsadit na odv\\u00e1\\u017en\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed kartu. M\\u00edsto toho, aby se soust\\u0159edil na vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed aktu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed generace konzol\\u00ed, co\\u017e jsme vid\\u011bli u modelu Xbox One X, obrac\\u00ed sv\\u00e9 \\u00fasil\\u00ed k v\\u00fdvoji zcela nov\\u00e9 generace za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"crgta\\">V centru t\\u00e9to strategie je touha p\\u0159in\\u00e9st technologick\\u00fd pr\\u016flom, kter\\u00fd je\\u0161t\\u011b nebyl v hern\\u00edm sv\\u011bt\\u011b zaznamen\\u00e1n. <b>Sarah Bond</b>, kter\\u00e1 stoj\\u00ed v \\u010dele Xboxu, ned\\u00e1vno potvrdila, \\u017ee nadch\\u00e1zej\\u00edc\\u00ed hardware p\\u0159inese hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm a v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016fm takov\\u00e9 mo\\u017enosti, o jak\\u00fdch se jim dosud ani nesnilo. Ambici\\u00f3zn\\u00ed c\\u00edl bude pravd\\u011bpodobn\\u011b dosa\\u017een prost\\u0159ednictv\\u00edm p