119	S pchodem PlayStation 5 Pro pichz i technologie PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR), kter by mohla leccos zmnit	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yebc7\\"><b>PSSR slibuje zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed sn\\u00edmkov\\u00e9 frekvence p\\u0159i zachov\\u00e1n\\u00ed kvality grafiky, co\\u017e m\\u016f\\u017ee p\\u0159in\\u00e9st v\\u00fdrazn\\u00e9 vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed hern\\u00edho z\\u00e1\\u017eitku bez nutnosti rozs\\u00e1hl\\u00fdch aktualizac\\u00ed pro ka\\u017edou hru.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"cj3u0\\"><b>PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution pozoruhodnou technologi\\u00ed</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"75d0g\\">Sony v\\u010dera kone\\u010dn\\u011b rozseklo v\\u0161echny spekulace a p\\u0159edstavilo dlouho o\\u010dek\\u00e1vanou <b>PlayStation 5 Pro</b>. Kone\\u010dn\\u011b je na sv\\u011bt\\u011b a te\\u010f se rozj\\u00ed\\u017ed\\u00ed debaty nejen o cen\\u011b, o kter\\u00e9 jsme u\\u017e psali <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"118\\"><b>ZDE</b></a>, ale hlavn\\u011b o specifikac\\u00edch a vylep\\u0161en\\u00edch, kter\\u00e1 s sebou p\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed. </p><p data-block-key=\\"8b1vi\\">Nejv\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00edm tah\\u00e1kem je bez pochyb technologie <b>PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR)</b>. D\\u00edky <b>um\\u011bl\\u00e9 inteligenci</b> zvl\\u00e1dne pokro\\u010dil\\u00fd <b>upscaling</b> obrazu, co\\u017e znamen\\u00e1 vy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed <b>framerate</b>, a p\\u0159itom \\u017e\\u00e1dn\\u00fd pokles v grafick\\u00e9 kvalit\\u011b. Podobnou funkci na PC m\\u016f\\u017eeme vid\\u011bt t\\u0159eba u <b>DLSS</b>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"18t3i\\">Co je na tom nejlep\\u0161\\u00ed? <b>PSSR</b> funguje i na hr\\u00e1ch, kter\\u00e9 nejsou p\\u0159\\u00edmo vylad\\u011bn\\u00e9 pro <b>PS5 Pro</b>, co\\u017e pot\\u011b\\u0161\\u00ed ka\\u017ed\\u00e9ho, kdo m\\u00e1 doma po\\u0159\\u00e1dnou hromadu star\\u0161\\u00edch titul\\u016f.</p>", "id": "29fdc24c-fbdf-49de-b104-c5e3626c2ca8"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "1226c2b8-f305-4d01-a97a-d13ece550ac6"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yebc7\\">Podle prvn\\u00edch dojm\\u016f z exkluzivn\\u00edho testu platformy <b>CNET</b> m\\u00e1 technologie PSSR fungovat nap\\u0159\\u00ed\\u010d celou knihovnou her pro PlayStation 5, ani\\u017e by bylo nutn\\u00e9, aby v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i vyd\\u00e1vali nov\\u00e9 patche. I tak p\\u0159i ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00edm uveden\\u00ed <b>PS5 Pro</b> na trh <b>7. listopadu 2024</b> se o\\u010dek\\u00e1v\\u00e1, \\u017ee a\\u017e <b>40 a\\u017e 50 her</b> obdr\\u017e\\u00ed speci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed <b>PS5 Pro</b> aktualizace. </p><p data-block-key=\\"ft3qn\\">Ale jak u\\u017e to b\\u00fdv\\u00e1, v\\u0161echno m\\u00e1 h\\u00e1\\u010dek. Trailer na <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"117\\"><b>PS5 Pro</b></a> nazna\\u010duje, \\u017ee <b>PSSR</b> bude dostupn\\u00e9 jen u n\\u011bkter\\u00fdch vybran\\u00fdch her, kter\\u00e9 projdou speci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed \\u00fapravou pro tuto konzoli. Na ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00ed vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159en\\u00ed od Sony se zat\\u00edm \\u010dek\\u00e1.</p><p data-block-key=\\"6sgja\\"><b>Co \\u0159\\u00edk\\u00e1te na novou konzoli? M\\u00e1te v pl\\u00e1nu si po\\u0159\\u00eddit? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f n\\u00ed\\u017ee.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6HaRMiTfvks\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"4oort\\"></p>", "id": "2f70e07e-78f3-4e94-b950-839f9484b149"}]	231	86	playstation, ps5 pro, sony, konzole, PSSR, PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution	\N	0	2	0
