151	Fntastic, studio stojc za hrou The Day Before, kter se stalo synonymem pro hern podvod, je zpt na scn s novou iniciativou Fntastic 2.0.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"wuijj\\"><b>Po katastrof\\u00e1ln\\u00edm vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed hry The Day Before a n\\u00e1sledn\\u00e9m zmizen\\u00ed ze sc\\u00e9ny se v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159sk\\u00e9 studio Fntastic op\\u011bt objevuje. </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"81gv9\\"><b>Fntastic se vrac\\u00ed, je \\u010das na odpu\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed?</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"885is\\"> M\\u00e1lokdo by \\u010dekal, \\u017ee se <b>Fntastic</b> po sv\\u00e9m skand\\u00e1lu vr\\u00e1t\\u00ed zp\\u011bt na hern\\u00ed sc\\u00e9nu. V prosinci 2023 kone\\u010dn\\u011b spat\\u0159ila sv\\u011btlo sv\\u011bta dlouho o\\u010dek\\u00e1van\\u00e1 hra <b>The Day Before</b>, kter\\u00e1 m\\u011bla b\\u00fdt velk\\u00fdm hitem mezi survivalov\\u00fdmi st\\u0159\\u00edle\\u010dkami. Nam\\u00edsto toho se v\\u0161ak uk\\u00e1zala jako naprost\\u00fd propad\\u00e1k. Hra byla pln\\u00e1 chyb a probl\\u00e9m\\u016f, kter\\u00e9 rychle vy\\u00fastily v jej\\u00ed sta\\u017een\\u00ed z trhu. K tomu v\\u0161emu studio <b>Fntastic</b> n\\u00e1sledn\\u011b zav\\u0159elo sv\\u00e9 dve\\u0159e a zd\\u00e1lo se, \\u017ee se s n\\u00edm hern\\u00ed sv\\u011bt rozlou\\u010dil nadobro.</p><p data-block-key=\\"836d5\\">Te\\u010f, t\\u00e9m\\u011b\\u0159 po roce, se <b>Fntastic</b> ne\\u010dekan\\u011b vrac\\u00ed s projektem nazvan\\u00fdm <b>\\u201eFntastic 2.0\\u201c</b>. Je to t\\u011b\\u017eko uv\\u011b\\u0159iteln\\u00e9, \\u0159ekli bychom a\\u017e drz\\u00e9. Nyn\\u00ed se v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i sna\\u017e\\u00ed z\\u00edskat zp\\u011bt d\\u016fv\\u011bru hern\\u00ed komunity t\\u00edm, \\u017ee p\\u0159izn\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed sv\\u00e9 chyby a slibuj\\u00ed zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "cc2bc4c0-8b7c-448b-97d1-6f65441222d8"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "8c7335c4-00a3-4b66-ae3c-2ab96f92515f"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"wuijj\\">V p\\u0159ekvapiv\\u00e9m p\\u0159\\u00edsp\\u011bvku na soci\\u00e1ln\\u00edch m\\u00e9di\\u00edch t\\u00fdm ozn\\u00e1mil, \\u017ee ka\\u017ed\\u00fd si zaslou\\u017e\\u00ed druhou \\u0161anci, a uvedl, \\u017ee pracuj\\u00ed na nov\\u00e9 h\\u0159e s n\\u00e1zvem <b>\\u201eEscape Factory\\u201c</b>.  Na jejich <a href=\\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fntasticgames/escape-factory\\"><b>Kickstarter</b> </a>kampa\\u0148 zat\\u00edm zareagovalo jen p\\u00e1r lid\\u00ed. Demo hry si v\\u0161ak m\\u016f\\u017eete st\\u00e1hnout nyn\\u00ed na Steamu (my v redakci ji\\u017e stahujeme). </p><p data-block-key=\\"27glj\\">Fntastic tak\\u00e9 odhalili sv\\u016fj nov\\u00fd pl\\u00e1n zam\\u011b\\u0159en\\u00fd na z\\u00edsk\\u00e1n\\u00ed d\\u016fv\\u011bry hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f prost\\u0159ednictv\\u00edm slibu poctivosti, transparentnosti a profesionality. Sou\\u010d\\u00e1st\\u00ed tohoto pl\\u00e1nu je tak\\u00e9 zve\\u0159ejn\\u011bn\\u00ed <a href=\\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/66cf2872c641a645890f1c5d/t/66e3f77eace4a55f13841699/1726216072958/Fntastic-2-0.pdf\\">whitepaperu</a>, kde se v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i zavazuj\\u00ed k tomu, \\u017ee zlep\\u0161\\u00ed sv\\u016fj p\\u0159\\u00edstup a komunikaci s komunitou. Mnoz\\u00ed z n\\u00e1s by v\\u0161ak ocenili, kdyby si tv\\u016frci uv\\u011bdomili nutnost t\\u011bchto zm\\u011bn je\\u0161t\\u011b p\\u0159ed samotn\\u00fdm vyd\\u00e1n\\u00edm <b>The Day Before</b>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"fssn1\\"><b>Co \\u0159\\u00edk\\u00e1te na probuzen\\u00ed studia  Fntastic? D\\u00e1te studiu je\\u0161t\\u011b \\u0161anci? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt n\\u00ed\\u017ee do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. Nev\\u00e1hejte se pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 na na\\u0161e nejnov\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed video.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxjZ13qz7Ys\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"4t7nf\\"></p>", "id": "bc220a70-042b-492f-ab0f-289a