126	Podle novch zprv Microsoft douf, e pidn Call of Duty do Game Passu vrazn zv poet pedplatitel. Vydn Black Ops 6 v rmci pedplatnho by mlo podpoit rst hernch pjm a pilkat nov uivatele	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"vz30s\\"><b>Rozhodnut\\u00ed p\\u0159idat Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 na Game Pass od prvn\\u00edho dne bylo pe\\u010dliv\\u011b zva\\u017eov\\u00e1no a nyn\\u00ed Microsoft spol\\u00e9h\\u00e1 na to, \\u017ee tento krok zv\\u00fd\\u0161\\u00ed jeho hern\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edjmy.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"e7msq\\"><b>Call of Duty: Black Ops 6 v Game Passu</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"9s1vf\\">Podle ned\\u00e1vn\\u00fdch zpr\\u00e1v se <b>Microsoft </b>rozhodl vsadit na za\\u0159azen\\u00ed nov\\u00e9 hry ze s\\u00e9rie Call of Duty, konkr\\u00e9tn\\u011b Black Ops 6, do sv\\u00e9 slu\\u017eby <b>Xbox Game Pass</b>, co\\u017e by m\\u011blo podpo\\u0159it r\\u016fst p\\u0159edplatitel\\u016f a zv\\u00fd\\u0161it hern\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edjmy. </p><p data-block-key=\\"5vrt8\\">Tom Warren z port\\u00e1lu The Verge uvedl, \\u017ee Microsoft dlouho zva\\u017eoval, zda m\\u00e1 Call of Duty za\\u0159adit do Game Passu hned v den jeho vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed, a nakonec se rozhodl zariskovat v nad\\u011bji, \\u017ee tento krok p\\u0159it\\u00e1hne nov\\u00e9 hr\\u00e1\\u010de.</p><p data-block-key=\\"alcp7\\">Microsoft v kv\\u011btnu 2024 ofici\\u00e1ln\\u011b ozn\\u00e1mil, \\u017ee Black Ops 6 bude dostupn\\u00e9 pro v\\u0161echny p\\u0159edplatitele <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"101\\"><b>Game Passu</b></a> ihned od prvn\\u00edho dne. Tento tah je historick\\u00fd, jeliko\\u017e jde o v\\u016fbec prvn\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edpad, kdy n\\u011bkter\\u00fd z d\\u00edl\\u016f t\\u00e9to ikonick\\u00e9 s\\u00e9rie zam\\u00ed\\u0159il do p\\u0159edplatitelsk\\u00e9 slu\\u017eby sou\\u010dasn\\u011b se sv\\u00fdm vyd\\u00e1n\\u00edm. </p><p data-block-key=\\"7959j\\">Jen dva m\\u011bs\\u00edce pot\\u00e9, co byla tato novinka odhalena, spole\\u010dnost ozn\\u00e1mila zv\\u00fd\\u0161en\\u00ed cen p\\u0159edplatn\\u00e9ho a\\u017e o 25 %. V \\u00fanoru t\\u00e9ho\\u017e roku dos\\u00e1hl po\\u010det p\\u0159edplatitel\\u016f Game Passu <b>34 milion\\u016f</b>, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e hr\\u00e1\\u010di si mohli vybrat ze t\\u0159\\u00ed r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch cenov\\u00fdch \\u00farovn\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "5d21bccc-4adb-48fc-b2dc-879e2ff23a54"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "bd8e5a01-8e9b-4807-bf42-309056f46121"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"vz30s\\">Microsoft zjevn\\u011b v\\u011b\\u0159\\u00ed, \\u017ee Call of Duty p\\u0159inese v\\u00fdznamn\\u00fd n\\u00e1r\\u016fst v po\\u010dtu p\\u0159edplatitel\\u016f a t\\u00edm i vy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edjmy. Zat\\u00edm v\\u0161ak nen\\u00ed jist\\u00e9, jak velk\\u00fd a hlavn\\u011b trval\\u00fd dopad tento krok bude m\\u00edt. O\\u010dek\\u00e1v\\u00e1 se, \\u017ee Black Ops 6 bude pro hr\\u00e1\\u010de siln\\u00fdm l\\u00e1kadlem, nicm\\u00e9n\\u011b ot\\u00e1zkou z\\u016fst\\u00e1v\\u00e1, zda tato strategie dok\\u00e1\\u017ee udr\\u017eet r\\u016fst p\\u0159edplatitel\\u016f i dlouhodob\\u011b. </p><p data-block-key=\\"926s9\\"><a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"82\\"><b>Call of Duty: Black Ops 6</b> </a>doraz\\u00ed ji\\u017e 25. \\u0159\\u00edjna na PC a konzole star\\u00e9 i nov\\u00e9 generace.</p><p data-block-key=\\"61amn\\"><b>M\\u00e1te v pl\\u00e1nu hr\\u00e1t nov\\u00fd d\\u00edl CoD v r\\u00e1mci p\\u0159edplatn\\u00e9ho Game Pass? Jak se t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edte na nov\\u00fd d\\u00edl? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f.</b></p>", "id": "d8168b23-637c-4f8a-beb6-c6de52902e24"}]	93	39	call of duty, microsoft, game pass, xbox, pedplatn, black ops 6	93	0	3	0
127	PlayStation 5 Pro pinese do her nejen vy vkon, ale tak zlepen vizuln kvality, a to i bez nutnosti aktualizac. Nkter hry vak budou z novho hardwaru tit vrazn vce ne jin.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"1pafj\\"><b>Nov\\u00fd PlayStation 5 Pro slibuje vylep\\u0161en\\u00fd v\\u00fdkon a vizu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed str\\u00e1nku her, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 tituly dos\\u00e1hnou znateln\\u00fdch zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed i bez speci\\u00e1ln\\u00edch patch\\u016f.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"9h0sd\\"><b>PlayStation 5 Pro m\\u00e1 nab\\u00eddnou vylep\\u0161en\\u00ed i bez patch\\u016f</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"a50um\\">Podcast <b>Digital Foundry</b> ned\\u00e1vno p\\u0159inesl exkluzivn\\u00ed informace o tom, jak si povedou hry na nov\\u00e9 konzoli <b>PlayStation 5 Pro</b>. Experti rozebrali ozn\\u00e1men\\u00ed konzole a odhalili zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 detaily o vylep\\u0161en\\u00edch, kter\\u00e1 m\\u016f\\u017eeme o\\u010dek\\u00e1vat. </p><p data-block-key=\\"7uh4j\\">Hry jako <b>The Last of Us Part 2</b> nebo<b> Ratchet &amp; Clank: Rift Apart</b>, exkluzivn\\u011b vytvo\\u0159en\\u00e9 pro PlayStation, se mohou t\\u011b\\u0161it na lep\\u0161\\u00ed kvalitu obrazu a stabiln\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed v\\u00fdkon d\\u00edky technologii <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/playstation-spectral-super-resolution-slibuje-zmenu-ale-skryva-jeden-hacek\\"><b>PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR)</b></a>. Horizon Forbidden West pob\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed s vy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00edmi detaily, ale rozli\\u0161en\\u00ed nedos\\u00e1hne pln\\u00fdch 4K, co\\u017e nazna\\u010duje, \\u017ee PSSR zde pravd\\u011bpodobn\\u011b nebylo pou\\u017eito.</p><p data-block-key=\\"72ano\\">U her od jin\\u00fdch studi\\u00ed ne\\u017e <b>Sony</b> je situace trochu jin\\u00e1. Nap\\u0159\\u00edklad Alan Wake 2 pob\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed ve stejn\\u00fdch rozli\\u0161en\\u00edch jako na z\\u00e1kladn\\u00edm modelu <b>PlayStation 5, </b>a to v<b> </b> 846p a 1260p. Zde pravd\\u011bpodobn\\u011b PSSR nahrazuje technologii AMD FSR 2. Re\\u017eim s 30 FPS by mohl obsahovat ray tracing (technologie pro realistick\\u00e9 zobrazen\\u00ed sv\\u011btla a st\\u00edn\\u016f), zat\\u00edmco u 60 FPS verze jsou p\\u0159\\u00edtomny odrazy generovan\\u00e9 pomoc\\u00ed screen-space technologi\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "38f0994c-c7cd-457f-98c7-8e1a2d50cc73"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "94c83962-94d8-47b7-945a-0cd0b0792635"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"1pafj\\">Velk\\u00e9 zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed \\u010dek\\u00e1 i <b>Hogwarts Legacy</b>, kter\\u00e9 na PlayStation 5 Pro p\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed ray-tracingov\\u00e9 odrazy a mo\\u017en\\u00e1 i st\\u00edny. Zaj\\u00edmav\\u00fdm p\\u0159\\u00edkladem je i Dragon\\u2019s Dogma 2, kter\\u00e9 vypad\\u00e1, \\u017ee pob\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed v 60 FPS s vyu\\u017eit\\u00edm PSSR. Titul Assassin\\u2019s Creed Mirage se zd\\u00e1, \\u017ee tak\\u00e9 b\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed v 60 FPS, ale v ni\\u017e\\u0161\\u00edm rozli\\u0161en\\u00ed 846p, kter\\u00e9 je n\\u00e1sledn\\u011b upscalovan\\u00e9 na vy\\u0161\\u0161\\u00ed d\\u00edky PSSR.</p><p data-block-key=\\"1lr1a\\"><b>Co \\u0159\\u00edk\\u00e1te na novou konzoli PlayStation 5 Pro? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. Nev\\u00e1hejte se n\\u00ed\\u017ee pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 na seznam her, kter\\u00e9 doraz\\u00ed v z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D1rjapqeyiw\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"7i4s7\\"></p>", "id": "2ca40842-1aa7-4640-b626-9b10ae79c099"}]	328	93		\N	0	1	0
88	Kad rok vyjde alespo jedna hra od velkho hernho vydavatele, kter se d povaovat za naprost propadk. Letos se tmto titulem s nejvy pravdpodobnost stala hra Concord, a m to sv dvody.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"5tueb\\"><b>Ka\\u017ed\\u00fd rok se objev\\u00ed alespo\\u0148 jedna hra od v\\u00fdznamn\\u00e9ho vydavatele, kterou lze ozna\\u010dit za \\u00fapln\\u00fd ne\\u00fasp\\u011bch. Letos tuto pochybnou poctu z\\u00edskala hra Concord, a nen\\u00ed to bezd\\u016fvodn\\u00e9.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"99ii\\"><b>Concord je solidn\\u00ed propad\\u00e1k a je k tomu p\\u00e1r d\\u016fvodu</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"374to\\">Na hern\\u00ed sc\\u00e9n\\u011b vznikaj\\u00ed stovky tis\\u00edc r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch her od studi\\u00ed r\\u016fzn\\u00e9 velikosti a od v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f s r\\u016fznou \\u00farovn\\u00ed zku\\u0161enost\\u00ed, kte\\u0159\\u00ed se sna\\u017e\\u00ed prosadit se sv\\u00fdm d\\u00edlem. N\\u011bkter\\u00fdm se to dokonce i poda\\u0159\\u00ed, ale pouze ve dvou p\\u0159\\u00edpadech: bu\\u010f vytvo\\u0159\\u00edte velmi dobrou hru, kterou si kritici i hr\\u00e1\\u010di chv\\u00e1l\\u00ed, i kdy\\u017e m\\u00e1 p\\u00e1r drobn\\u00fdch nedostatk\\u016f, nebo vytvo\\u0159\\u00edte extr\\u00e9mn\\u011b \\u0161patnou hru, u kter\\u00e9 se hr\\u00e1\\u010dsk\\u00e1 komunita pt\\u00e1, co v\\u00e1s vlastn\\u011b napadlo.</p><p data-block-key=\\"5kgni\\">Leto\\u0161n\\u00ed rok se kandid\\u00e1tem na nejv\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed propad\\u00e1k roku 2024 stalo pr\\u00e1v\\u011b nov\\u00e9 studio <b>Firewalk</b> se svou hrou <b>Concord</b>, kter\\u00e1 vznikla pod k\\u0159\\u00eddly <b>Sony</b>. Ale pro\\u010d je tento titul takov\\u00fd propad\\u00e1k?</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xQB_2FF2G1o\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"e76kq\\"></p>", "id": "30056ee0-5a98-4b35-84ef-6a90ba824f4a"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "cd5c04ff-2112-4f4a-86ab-275a319d6f72"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"5tueb\\"><b>Pro\\u010d je to takov\\u00fd pr\\u016f\\u0161vih?</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"dvoum\\">Ne\\u017e se do toho pust\\u00edme, m\\u016fj n\\u00e1zor je \\u010dist\\u011b m\\u016fj osobn\\u00ed pohled jako hr\\u00e1\\u010de, kter\\u00fd se v hern\\u00edm sv\\u011bt\\u011b pohybuje u\\u017e n\\u011bkolik let. Kdy\\u017e tohle m\\u00e1me ujasn\\u011bn\\u00e9, poj\\u010fme se na to pod\\u00edvat bl\\u00ed\\u017ee.</p>", "id": "b088d8be-3144-4a49-ac3a-c7121f7a6267"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"11ttj\\"><b>Gameplay bez inovace</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"9b7a2\\"><b>Concord</b> m\\u00e1 opravdu mnoho nedostatk\\u016f, ale zam\\u011b\\u0159\\u00edm se na ty nejm\\u00e9n\\u011b v\\u00fdrazn\\u00e9. Prvn\\u00edm z nich je samotn\\u00fd gameplay, kter\\u00fd je paradoxn\\u011b asi tou nejm\\u00e9n\\u011b problematickou \\u010d\\u00e1st\\u00ed cel\\u00e9 hry. V podstat\\u011b se jedn\\u00e1 o klasick\\u00fd multiplayerov\\u00fd hero-shooter, prezentovan\\u00fd jako live service hra. Bohu\\u017eel, Concord nep\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed t\\u00e9m\\u011b\\u0159 \\u017e\\u00e1dnou inovaci oproti ostatn\\u00edm hr\\u00e1m v tomto \\u017e\\u00e1nru, a nab\\u00eddka hern\\u00edch m\\u00f3d\\u016f je sotva pr\\u016fm\\u011brn\\u00e1.</p><p data-block-key=\\"9k5cs\\">Samotn\\u00e9 j\\u00e1dro gameplaye je prakticky identick\\u00e9 s tituly jako <b>Overwatch</b> nebo <b>Paladins</b>, bez jak\\u00e9koliv snahy o odli\\u0161en\\u00ed. Ka\\u017ed\\u00fd hrdina m\\u00e1 pouze dv\\u011b aktivn\\u00ed schopnosti a dv\\u011b zbran\\u011b na v\\u00fdm\\u011bnu, co\\u017e je naprosto standardn\\u00ed nastaven\\u00ed bez jak\\u00e9koliv originality. A pr\\u00e1v\\u011b tady nast\\u00e1v\\u00e1 k\\u00e1men \\u00farazu. Hra rychle omrz\\u00ed a nenab\\u00edz\\u00ed \\u017e\\u00e1dn\\u00fd d\\u016fvod, pro\\u010d byste v n\\u00ed m\\u011bli tr\\u00e1vit des\\u00edtky hodin.</p><p data-block-key=\\"fmrjl\\">Ani p\\u0159\\u00edb\\u011bh, kter\\u00fd v\\u00e1s hrou prov\\u00e1z\\u00ed, nep\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed nic, co by v\\u00e1s udr\\u017eelo. Podle mnoh\\u00fdch hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f je naprosto ot\\u0159esn\\u00fd, co\\u017e je\\u0161t\\u011b v\\u00edce p\\u0159isp\\u00edv\\u00e1 k celkov\\u00e9mu zklam\\u00e1n\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "86295dbd-88fb-4e8f-8f3e-65dd564ed175"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "5bce491e-fecc-4c25-9efe-c3d6c0dc1fa3"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"11ttj\\"><b>Ot\\u0159esn\\u00e9 UI</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"ep26r\\">Druh\\u00fdm a v\\u00fdrazn\\u011b bij\\u00edc\\u00edm probl\\u00e9mem je u\\u017eivatelsk\\u00e9 rozhran\\u00ed hry, kter\\u00e9 je jednodu\\u0161e \\u0159e\\u010deno amat\\u00e9rsky zpracovan\\u00e9 a p\\u016fsob\\u00ed, jako by tv\\u016frci UI nepochopili, na kterou platformu se hra vyv\\u00edj\\u00ed. Nesmysln\\u011b velk\\u00e9 ikony schopnost\\u00ed a zbran\\u00ed, stejn\\u011b jako ukazatele jednotliv\\u00fdch t\\u00fdm\\u016f, objektiv\\u016f a po\\u010dtu smrt\\u00ed, jsou naprosto nevhodn\\u00e9 a p\\u016fsob\\u00ed sp\\u00ed\\u0161e ru\\u0161iv\\u011b ne\\u017e p\\u0159ehledn\\u011b. Celkov\\u00fd dojem z <b>UI</b> je, \\u017ee se jedn\\u00e1 o pr\\u00e1ci odvedenou narychlo a bez hlub\\u0161\\u00edho zamy\\u0161len\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"av2jt\\">Ani menu na tom nen\\u00ed o moc l\\u00e9pe; v\\u0161e nasv\\u011bd\\u010duje tomu, \\u017ee <b>Concord</b> m\\u011bl b\\u00fdt p\\u016fvodn\\u011b mobiln\\u00edm titulem, ale n\\u011bjak\\u00fdm zp\\u016fsobem se tv\\u016frci UI nedozv\\u011bd\\u011bli o zm\\u011bn\\u011b platformy. V\\u00fdsledek je tedy UI, kter\\u00e9 p\\u016fsob\\u00ed neprofesion\\u00e1ln\\u011b a nezapad\\u00e1 do kontextu hry. Ud\\u011blejte si vlastn\\u00ed n\\u00e1zor.</p><embed embedtype=\\"image\\" format=\\"left\\" id=\\"53\\" alt=\\"Concord UI\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"7nnrm\\"></p>", "id": "4f6304d0-a230-40a1-9484-e379d8bbd7fb"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"11ttj\\"><b>Agresivn\\u00ed politick\\u00e1 propaganda</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"2kuc7\\">A jako posledn\\u00ed v\\u011bc mus\\u00edm zm\\u00ednit mo\\u017en\\u00e1 nejo\\u017eehav\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed t\\u00e9ma, kter\\u00e9 \\u0159adu hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f na Concordu irituje je nesnesiteln\\u00e1 p\\u0159emr\\u0161t\\u011bnost politick\\u00e9 propagace v r\\u00e1mci hrateln\\u00fdch postav.</p><p data-block-key=\\"f9o6v\\">Mnoz\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010di si st\\u011b\\u017euj\\u00ed, \\u017ee postavy jsou neatraktivn\\u00ed, ploch\\u00e9 a zd\\u00e1 se, \\u017ee byly zahrnuty do hry jen proto, aby splnily n\\u011bjak\\u00e9 politick\\u00e9 kv\\u00f3ty. Up\\u0159\\u00edmn\\u011b, mus\\u00edm s t\\u00edm souhlasit. Skoro \\u017e\\u00e1dn\\u00e1 postava nen\\u00ed skute\\u010dn\\u011b zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e1, a u ka\\u017ed\\u00e9 z nich jsou uvedeny jejich <i>\\"pronouns\\"</i>, co\\u017e je n\\u011bco, co my hr\\u00e1\\u010di (\\u010dti drtiv\\u00e1 v\\u011bt\\u0161ina) ve hr\\u00e1ch nechceme \\u0159e\\u0161it, zvl\\u00e1\\u0161t\\u011b kdy\\u017e toho m\\u00e1me dost i v re\\u00e1ln\\u00e9m sv\\u011bt\\u011b.</p><p data-block-key=\\"e6u9d\\">Kontroverze panuje i kolem \\u00fadajn\\u00e9mu toxick\\u00e9mu prost\\u0159ed\\u00ed ve studiu. Podle youtubera Smash JT a anonymn\\u00edho zdroje v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159ka <b>Lisa Brown</b>, kter\\u00e1 se identifikuje jako nebin\\u00e1rn\\u00ed, po\\u017eaduje, aby ji kolegov\\u00e9 oslovovali titulem <i>\\"profesor\\"</i>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"1t3io\\">Brown \\u00fadajn\\u011b prosazovala sv\\u00e9 politick\\u00e9 n\\u00e1zory, nen\\u00e1vid\\u011bla zbran\\u011b a dokonce po\\u017eadovala propu\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00ed neo\\u010dkovan\\u00fdch zam\\u011bstnanc\\u016f. Celkov\\u011b to v\\u0161e p\\u016fsob\\u00ed sp\\u00ed\\u0161e jako politick\\u00fd vzkaz od v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f ne\\u017e jako skute\\u010dn\\u011b promy\\u0161len\\u00e1 hra. Ale klidn\\u011b si ud\\u011blejte vlastn\\u00ed n\\u00e1zor.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SakVQnpbjvM\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"a8hg0\\"></p>", "id": "e48e42ef-6e8f-4027-a150-3a2009629c99"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "5284fbcc-727f-476e-877e-2f8e782ae333"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"11ttj\\"><b>P\\u0159edur\\u010den k z\\u00e1niku</b></h3><p data-block-key=\\"387mj\\">Titul m\\u00e1 samoz\\u0159ejm\\u011b mnohem v\\u00edce probl\\u00e9m\\u016f. Mezi nimi je nap\\u0159\\u00edklad p\\u0159emr\\u0161t\\u011bn\\u00e1 cena za velmi m\\u00e1lo obsahu, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e hra nav\\u00edc obsahuje obchod s mikrotransakcemi.</p><p data-block-key=\\"75j28\\">Dal\\u0161\\u00edm velk\\u00fdm probl\\u00e9mem je \\u0161patn\\u00e1 optimalizace na n\\u011bkter\\u00fdch za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00edch a mno\\u017estv\\u00ed dal\\u0161\\u00edch chyb, kter\\u00e9 by sp\\u00ed\\u0161e odpov\\u00eddaly pr\\u00e1ci za\\u010d\\u00ednaj\\u00edc\\u00edch v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. Co je v\\u0161ak zar\\u00e1\\u017eej\\u00edc\\u00ed, je skute\\u010dnost, \\u017ee studio Firewalk m\\u00e1 podle n\\u011bkter\\u00fdch ve sv\\u00fdch \\u0159ad\\u00e1ch zku\\u0161en\\u00e9 v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159e, kte\\u0159\\u00ed pracovali na n\\u011bkolika d\\u00edlech<a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"86\\"><b> Call of Duty</b></a>. Nav\\u00edc se chlub\\u00ed t\\u00edm, \\u017ee na h\\u0159e pracovali osm let a \\u017ee do v\\u00fdvoje bylo investov\\u00e1no zna\\u010dn\\u00e9 mno\\u017estv\\u00ed pen\\u011bz.</p><p data-block-key=\\"9prsh\\">Zkr\\u00e1tka a dob\\u0159e, hra je p\\u0159edur\\u010dena k rychl\\u00e9mu a bezbolestn\\u00e9mu z\\u00e1niku. Tento osud potvrzuj\\u00ed jak u\\u017eivatelsk\\u00e1 hodnocen\\u00ed na <a href=\\"https://www.metacritic.com/game/concord/\\"><b>Metacritics</b></a>. Hra dosahuje u\\u017eivatelsk\\u00e9ho hodnocen\\u00ed pouh\\u00fdch 1,9/10. Co se t\\u00fd\\u010de po\\u010dtu hr\\u00e1\\u01