134	Ubisoft oznmil novou firemn politiku, kter vyaduje, aby zamstnanci trvili minimln ti dny tdn v kanceli. Tento krok m podpoit kreativitu a tmovou spoluprci.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yffp7\\"><b>Nov\\u00e1 politika Ubisoftu stanovuje, \\u017ee zam\\u011bstnanci mus\\u00ed pracovat v kancel\\u00e1\\u0159i alespo\\u0148 t\\u0159i dny t\\u00fddn\\u011b, aby se zv\\u00fd\\u0161ila produktivita a podpo\\u0159ila spolupr\\u00e1ce.  </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"9mkvp\\"><b>Ubisoft v probl\\u00e9mech?</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"2uhge\\"><b>Ubisoft</b> ozn\\u00e1mil z\\u00e1sadn\\u00ed zm\\u011bnu ve sv\\u00e9 pracovn\\u00ed politice. V\\u0161ichni zam\\u011bstnanci nyn\\u00ed budou muset tr\\u00e1vit alespo\\u0148 <b>t\\u0159i dny v t\\u00fddnu</b> v kancel\\u00e1\\u0159i. C\\u00edlem t\\u00e9to politiky je pos\\u00edlit kreativitu a t\\u00fdmovou spolupr\\u00e1ci, co\\u017e by m\\u011blo v\\u00e9st k v\\u00fdvoji je\\u0161t\\u011b kvalitn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00edch her pro n\\u00e1s, hr\\u00e1\\u010de. Aneb tak to uv\\u00e1d\\u00ed Ubisoft.</p><p data-block-key=\\"b0jie\\">Marie-Sophie de Waubert, \\u0159editelka studi\\u00ed a portfolia Ubisoftu, v e-mailu zam\\u011bstnanc\\u016fm uvedla: <i>\\u201eJsme kreativn\\u00ed spole\\u010dnost a kreativita nejv\\u00edce kvete p\\u0159i osobn\\u00edch setk\\u00e1n\\u00edch, neform\\u00e1ln\\u00edch rozhovorech a spolupr\\u00e1ci tv\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed v tv\\u00e1\\u0159. Osobn\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edtomnost tak\\u00e9 urychluje \\u0159e\\u0161en\\u00ed probl\\u00e9m\\u016f a zlep\\u0161uje rozhodov\\u00e1n\\u00ed. V rychle se m\\u011bn\\u00edc\\u00edm hern\\u00edm sv\\u011bt\\u011b je kl\\u00ed\\u010dov\\u00e9, abychom se u\\u010dili jeden od druh\\u00e9ho, zejm\\u00e9na nov\\u00e1\\u010dci, kte\\u0159\\u00ed se pot\\u0159ebuj\\u00ed rychle zorientovat.\\u201c </i></p>", "id": "33c0f5cf-b9bb-4e1f-8eae-8828eaec030d"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "919daec6-a89d-4702-86e1-623044e60cfa"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yffp7\\">Spole\\u010dnost v\\u0161ak zd\\u016fraz\\u0148uje, \\u017ee ch\\u00e1pe individu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed situace sv\\u00fdch zam\\u011bstnanc\\u016f. <b>Ubisoft </b>rozhodn\\u011b nen\\u00ed jedin\\u00fd, kdo se vrac\\u00ed k pr\\u00e1ci v kancel\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00edch. Podobn\\u00e9 kroky podnikly i dal\\u0161\\u00ed technologick\\u00e9 firmy jako <b>Amazon</b>, <b>Dell</b> nebo <b>AT&amp;T</b>. </p><p data-block-key=\\"26fg6\\"><a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/akcie-ubisoftu-opet-vyrazne-klesly-nejistota-roste\\"><b>Ubisoft</b></a> aktu\\u00e1ln\\u011b \\u010del\\u00ed v\\u00fdrazn\\u00e9mu poklesu akci\\u00ed, co\\u017e vedlo n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 investory k otev\\u0159en\\u00e9 kritice veden\\u00ed a po\\u017eadavk\\u016fm na zm\\u011bny ve spole\\u010dnosti. Situaci d\\u00e1le zhor\\u0161uj\\u00ed posledn\\u00ed tituly, jako je ned\\u00e1vno vydan\\u00e1 hra <b>Star Wars Outlaws</b>, kter\\u00e1 nedok\\u00e1zala dos\\u00e1hnout v\\u00fdrazn\\u00fdch prodej\\u016f ani vysok\\u00e9ho hodnocen\\u00ed. Ne\\u00fasp\\u011bch zvy\\u0161uje tlak na spole\\u010dnost. O\\u010di n\\u00e1s hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f se nyn\\u00ed up\\u00ednaj\\u00ed na <b>Assassin's Creed Shadows, kter\\u00fd m\\u00e1 dorazit ji\\u017e 15. listopadu leto\\u0161n\\u00edho roku.</b></p>", "id": "abd044cd-2cfa-4d2c-941d-387a2fa8e2a3"}]	38	100	ubisoft, firma, hry, politika	\N	0	0	0
31	O vkendu 13. a 14. dubna jsme se zastnili akce v ostravskm E-Motion Parku hernho veletrhu OvaGames. Jak se nm akce lbila?	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"mcr8v\\">V\\u00edkend 13. na 14. dubna se nesl ve znamen\\u00ed ostravsk\\u00e9ho hern\\u00edho veletrhu OvaGames. Jako\\u017eto partne\\u0159i akce jsme tam nemohli chyb\\u011bt.</p><p data-block-key=\\"q4co\\"><b>Hern\\u00ed veletrh OvaGames</b></p><p data-block-key=\\"adekh\\">T\\u00fdm Superpa\\u0159meni zam\\u00ed\\u0159il na hern\\u00ed veletrh v Ostrav\\u011b. A\\u017e z \\u010cesk\\u00fdch Bud\\u011bjovic, p\\u0159es ot\\u0159esnou D1 daleko na v\\u00fdchod. Po p\\u0159\\u00edjezdu na parkovi\\u0161t\\u011b p\\u0159ed E-Motion Park jsme byli p\\u0159ekvapeni jeho t\\u00e9m\\u011b\\u0159 pr\\u00e1zdnou plochou. N\\u00e1\\u0161 dojem se v\\u0161ak okam\\u017eit\\u011b zm\\u011bnil, kdy\\u017e jsme prostoupili skrze br\\u00e1nu s bannerem nesouc\\u00ed n\\u00e1zev 'Vstup na hern\\u00ed veletrh'. P\\u0159iv\\u00edtaly n\\u00e1s usm\\u011bvav\\u00e9 sle\\u010dny, dostali jsme visa\\u010dky a pln\\u00ed o\\u010dek\\u00e1v\\u00e1n\\u00ed vykro\\u010dili vp\\u0159ed.</p>", "id": "2981cec4-c2b9-4c8c-9055-9b18267b51b4"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "dc5e83af-e8c6-4fa8-903c-a9d3db51a2ea"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"mcr8v\\">Na za\\u010d\\u00e1tku n\\u00e1s zaujalo mno\\u017estv\\u00ed po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010d\\u016f a hern\\u00edch konzol\\u00ed k dispozici. I kdy\\u017e jsme p\\u0159ijeli kr\\u00e1tce p\\u0159ed polednem, m\\u00edsto bylo ji\\u017e pln\\u00e9 n\\u00e1v\\u0161t\\u011bvn\\u00edk\\u016f, t\\u00e9m\\u011b\\u0159 ka\\u017ed\\u00e1 hern\\u00ed ma\\u0161ina obsazena. Na\\u0161t\\u011bst\\u00ed jsme se nemuseli p\\u0159\\u00edli\\u0161 dlouho zdr\\u017eovat \\u010dek\\u00e1n\\u00edm, proto\\u017ee n\\u00e1v\\u0161t\\u011bvn\\u00edci se u za\\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed pravideln\\u011b st\\u0159\\u00eddali. Hned u vstupu se nach\\u00e1zel st\\u00e1nek 'Hraju hokej', kde na gau\\u010d\\u00edch mohl kdokoliv vyzvat protihr\\u00e1\\u010de k souboji v NHL. Nedaleko se nach\\u00e1zela k\\u0159esla obklopuj\\u00edc\\u00ed legend\\u00e1rn\\u00ed konzoli PlayStation 2. Po prav\\u00e9 stran\\u011b pod\\u00e9l zd\\u00ed se rozkl\\u00e1daly stanice s virtu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed realitou a kousek d\\u00e1le simul\\u00e1tory \\u0159\\u00edzen\\u00ed s hrou Forza Horizon. D\\u00e1le jsme narazili na n\\u011bkolik \\u0159ad PC. Na lev\\u00e9 stran\\u011b se t\\u00e1hl parket, u kter\\u00e9ho st\\u00e1l st\\u00e1nek s bohat\\u011b z\\u00e1sobenou tombolou. Kv\\u016fli lep\\u0161\\u00edmu p\\u0159ehledu o veletrhu jsme se vypravili do patra. Zde krom\\u011b modern\\u00edch po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010d\\u016f byl i st\\u00e1nek s hrou Mafia, a star\\u00e9 po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010de, na kter\\u00fdch si n\\u00e1v\\u0161t\\u011bvn\\u00edci mohli zahr\\u00e1t klasiky jako Moorhuhn nebo Bul\\u00e1nci.</p>", "id": "029828af-acb5-4777-9d20-25a932509593"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "d7906dde-c661-4c3c-a557-c1ee29fd7e76"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yy5wq\\">Ti, kte\\u0159\\u00ed si zakoupili VIP vstup, m\\u011bli p\\u0159\\u00edstup do prostoru s pohodln\\u00fdmi gau\\u010di, kde si mohli vybrat n\\u00e1poje z lednice, uva\\u0159it k\\u00e1vu nebo \\u010daj a ochutnat chleb\\u00ed\\u010dky a celkov\\u011b tak ulevit sv\\u00fdm nachozen\\u00fdm noh\\u00e1m. Z patra jsme m\\u011bli v\\u00fdhled na cel\\u00fd are\\u00e1l. D\\u011bti se roztrou\\u0161en\\u011b motaly mezi st\\u00e1nky v hled\\u00e1n\\u00ed voln\\u00e9ho po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010de, zat\\u00edmco skupinky hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f se sch\\u00e1zely u hern\\u00edch stanovi\\u0161\\u0165. Cosplayerky dod\\u00e1valy atmosf\\u00e9\\u0159e pestr\\u00fd n\\u00e1dech. N\\u00e1v\\u0161t\\u011bvn\\u00edci se shlukovali kolem PC a konzol\\u00ed a zapojili se do \\u017eiv\\u00fdch konverzac\\u00ed. Zvuky hlas\\u016f se prol\\u00ednaly s ozn\\u00e1men\\u00edmi z mikrofonu na parketu, kde pr\\u00e1v\\u011b prob\\u00edhal n\\u011bjak\\u00fd turnaj, a v pozad\\u00ed zn\\u011bly zvuky z\\u00e1vod\\u016f motok\\u00e1r.</p>", "id": "c5434dff-6a16-4862-b377-08e8c90e6239"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "4c44a119-cdc0-4704-9145-19f4e8220ad1"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yy5wq\\">Rozhodli jsme se pokra\\u010dovat d\\u00e1le, sestoupili po schodech dol\\u016f, kdy\\u017e hned po levici se rozl\\u00e9hal zaj\\u00edmav\\u00fd ly\\u017ea\\u0159sk\\u00fd simul\\u00e1tor, kter\\u00e9ho jsme si p\\u016fvodn\\u011b nev\\u0161imli. Atrakce jako stvo\\u0159en\\u00e1 pro milovn\\u00edky horsk\\u00fdch svah\\u016f, kte\\u0159\\u00ed si letos kv\\u016fli po\\u010das\\u00ed na skute\\u010dn\\u00e9 sjezdovky nemohli zajet. Jeliko\\u017e nikdo z n\\u00e1s ly\\u017ea\\u0159i, pokra\\u010dovali jsme d\\u00e1le vzad. Po na\\u0161\\u00ed levici nach\\u00e1zely stanovi\\u0161t\\u011b cosplayerky v detailn\\u011b propracovan\\u00fdch kost\\u00fdmech. Naproti n\\u00e1m l\\u00e1kav\\u011b vykukoval bar Murloc, kde n\\u00e1s sympatick\\u00fd mlad\\u00edk zval k rulet\\u011b o pan\\u00e1ky. Nikdo z n\\u00e1s nezav\\u00e1hal. Zapojili jsme se, popov\\u00eddali o veletrhu a ochutnali n\\u011bkolik vynikaj\\u00edc\\u00edch drink\\u016f z jejich rozmanit\\u00e9 nab\\u00eddky.</p>", "id": "8d5b74da-78df-4e82-8587-474c7d081d52"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "705a6d66-929d-45e9-a0ce-e21e3b8c0965"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yy5wq\\">Pr\\u016fzkumn\\u00e1 cesta pokra\\u010dovala za barem, kde se otev\\u0159el prostor pln\\u00fd po\\u010d\\u00edta\\u010d\\u016f a stol\\u016f na beer pong. V tomto zadn\\u00edm \\u00faseku veletrhu dr\\u017eel sv\\u00e9 k\\u0159\\u00eddlo t\\u00fdm Fly5esports, kter\\u00fd zde po\\u0159\\u00e1dal n\\u011bkolik turnaj\\u016f pro n\\u00e1v\\u0161t\\u011bvn\\u00edky veletrhu, t\\u0159eba v popul\\u00e1rn\\u00edm League of Legends, jeho\\u017e se \\u00fa\\u010dastnil i n\\u00e1mi vybran\\u00fd \\u010dlen.</p><p data-block-key=\\"ffg42\\">Zklam\\u00e1n\\u00edm pro m\\u011b nastala situace, kdy\\u017e jsem se minul s v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i z Perun Creative, zn\\u00e1m\\u00fd svou hrou Hobo: Tough Life, a novinkou Kvark. Na druhou stranu jsme se setkali s hv\\u011bzdami legend\\u00e1rn\\u00edch film\\u016f P\\u00e1rty H\\u00e1rd a P\\u00e1rty H\\u00e1rder: Summer Massacre, Ji\\u0159\\u00edm Bohat\\u00fdm a Danielem \\u017d\\u00e1\\u010dkem. Nezapomn\\u011bli jsme se vyfotit ani s herci z MAFIA: The City of Gamers.</p>", "id": "f94c1a3c-a95c-45e3-895a-18fa1b332099"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "856da6d5-f3f6-43c1-9faf-81bc64de49f4"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"yy5wq\\">Od her jako Fortnite, League of Legends a Counter-Strike jsme se pustili i do r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch simul\\u00e1tor\\u016f. U\\u017eili si j\\u00edzdu ve Forza Horizon, kde jsme m\\u00edsto my\\u0161i s kl\\u00e1vesnice ovl\\u00e1dali klasick\\u00e9 ped\\u00e1ly a volant. Nevynechali jsme ani virtu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed realitu, zahr\\u00e1li si na konzol\\u00edch, vyzvali soupe\\u0159e v Bul\\u00e1nc\\u00edch a jako t\\u00fdm jsme se vydali na j\\u00edzdu v elektrick\\u00fdch motok\\u00e1r\\u00e1ch. Nechyb\\u011bl ani beerpong \\u010di \\u0161achy. Poznali jsme nov\\u00e9 lidi, dozv\\u011bd\\u011bli se n\\u011bco nov\\u00e9ho.</p><p data-block-key=\\"d6kdh\\">Jak bychom tedy ohodnotili hern\\u00ed veletrh OvaGames? Druh\\u00fd den p\\u0159i n\\u00e1vratu dom\\u016f jsme jednomysln\\u011b do\\u0161li k z\\u00e1v\\u011bru, \\u017ee se jedn\\u00e1 o vynikaj\\u00edc\\u00ed hern\\u00ed akci. OvaGames je skv\\u011bl\\u00e1 p\\u0159\\u00edle\\u017eitost pro z\\u00e1bavu a setk\\u00e1n\\u00ed s \\u00fa\\u017easn\\u00fdmi lidmi. S nad\\u0161en\\u00edm se t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edme na p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u00ed rok, kdy se na veletrh op\\u011bt vyprav\\u00edme. Mo\\u017en\\u00e1 pro v\\u00e1s p\\u0159\\u00ed\\u0161t\\u011b p\\u0159ichyst\\u00e1me i mal\\u00e9 p\\u0159ekvapen\\u00ed. D\\u00edky OvaGames!</p><p data-block-key=\\"3pmev\\">P\\u0159ipravili jsme pro v\\u00e1s tak\\u00e9 kr\\u00e1tk\\u00e9 video, kter\\u00e9 v\\u00e1m uk\\u00e1\\u017ee, co v\\u0161echno m\\u016f\\u017eete na veletrhu objevit, co jsme zde za\\u017eili a co vid\\u011bli. Nezapome\\u0148te se na n\\u011bj pod\\u00edvat n\\u00ed\\u017ee. Budeme tak\\u00e9 r\\u00e1di za like a odb\\u011br.</p><p data-block-key=\\"1m051\\"></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wMsfDxBGTUY\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"15ahf\\"></p>", "id": "6bab6629-c388-4d3a-9eae-7aad21ee2071"}]	37	8	ovagames	\N	0	7	0
