163	Posledn tdny se kolem hry Palworld dlo dosti vc, kter by mohli zsadn ovlivnit hru a jej vvoje. Co ve se vlastn udlo?	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"fdpw1\\"><b>Posledn\\u00ed t\\u00fddny se kolem hry Palworld ud\\u00e1lo mnoho v\\u011bc\\u00ed, kter\\u00e9 by mohly z\\u00e1sadn\\u011b ovlivnit jak samotnou hru, tak jej\\u00ed v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159e. Co se tedy vlastn\\u011b stalo? </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"d3dd5\\"><b>Novinky o h\\u0159e Palworld</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"232hs\\">V posledn\\u00ed dob\\u011b jsme sly\\u0161eli \\u0159adu zaj\\u00edmav\\u00fdch informac\\u00ed o h\\u0159e <b>Palworld</b>. N\\u011bkter\\u00e9 z nich byly pozitivn\\u00ed a povzbudiv\\u00e9, zat\\u00edmco jin\\u00e9 byly nep\\u0159\\u00edjemn\\u00e9 a mohly by ohrozit samotn\\u00e9 studio Pocketpair. Poj\\u010fme si to tedy postupn\\u011b proj\\u00edt. </p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv5t1ycoLaM\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"f7gu\\"></p>", "id": "e8b18c59-2395-4e27-870c-494d9c28fc02"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "2947647f-d8fa-4bbe-a1d0-f0968c062f20"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"fdpw1\\">\\u017daloba od Nintenda</h3><p data-block-key=\\"ffd03\\">Dlouho se o tom spekulovalo a vtipkovalo, a\\u017e se to nakonec stalo. Velk\\u00e9 Nintendo spole\\u010dn\\u011b s <b>The Pok\\u00e9mon Company</b> za\\u017ealovaly studio Pocketpair u soudu v Tokiu. A pro\\u010d? Jde o poru\\u0161en\\u00ed ochrann\\u00e9ho patentu, kter\\u00fd ob\\u011b spole\\u010dnosti vlastn\\u00ed, ale o jak\\u00fd p\\u0159esn\\u00fd patent se jedn\\u00e1, netu\\u0161\\u00ed ani majitel<b> Pocketpair</b>, Takuro Mizobe. Mnoho lid\\u00ed na internetu se domn\\u00edv\\u00e1, \\u017ee jde o mechaniku h\\u00e1zen\\u00ed Pal Sphere, kter\\u00e1 n\\u00e1padn\\u011b p\\u0159ipom\\u00edn\\u00e1 Pok\\u00e9bally. <i>Bohu\\u017eel v\\u0161ak nem\\u00e1me potvrzeno, zda je tato informace zcela pravdiv\\u00e1.</i></p><p