186	Hitpoint, nejznmj esk organiztor turnaj League of Legends, se v posledn dob potk s nepjemnmi okolnostmi. Dvodem jsou kontroverze, kter se vynoily bhem nedvnch dn. Co pesn se stalo?	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"vkb9g\\"><b>Hitpoint, vedouc\\u00ed \\u010desk\\u00fd organiz\\u00e1tor turnaj\\u016f League of Legends, proch\\u00e1z\\u00ed t\\u011b\\u017ek\\u00fdm obdob\\u00edm kv\\u016fli skand\\u00e1lu, kter\\u00fd vy\\u0161el najevo v posledn\\u00edch dnech. Co se p\\u0159esn\\u011b stalo? </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"41i8e\\"><b>Kauza kolem \\u010desk\\u00e9 organizace Hitpoint</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"ao7u\\">Hitpoint, \\u010desk\\u00e1 organizace zn\\u00e1m\\u00e1 po\\u0159\\u00e1d\\u00e1n\\u00edm a vys\\u00edl\\u00e1n\\u00edm lok\\u00e1ln\\u00edch turnaj\\u016f League of Legends a zprost\\u0159edkov\\u00e1n\\u00edm evropsk\\u00e9 ligy s \\u010desk\\u00fdm koment\\u00e1\\u0159em, m\\u00e1 za sebou v\\u00edce ne\\u017e 15 let historie. D\\u00edky jej\\u00ed \\u010dinnosti se mnoho \\u010desk\\u00fdch hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f prosadilo na profesion\\u00e1ln\\u00ed \\u00farovni a \\u0159ada mlad\\u00fdch lid\\u00ed dostala \\u0161anci rozjet kari\\u00e9ru v r\\u016fzn\\u00fdch hern\\u00edch odv\\u011btv\\u00edch. Nyn\\u00ed v\\u0161ak organizace proch\\u00e1z\\u00ed slo\\u017eit\\u00fdm obdob\\u00edm kv\\u016fli eskaluj\\u00edc\\u00ed kauze, kter\\u00e1 organizaci st\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed osv\\u011btluje v dobr\\u00e9m sv\\u011btle. Co se ale p\\u0159esn\\u011b stalo? </p>", "id": "57447a2a-7d1d-4def-b523-407f48d7b134"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "e8f13511-4989-480d-868c-eb5481516cf4"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"vkb9g\\">Jak to za\\u010dalo?</h3><p data-block-key=\\"8fnlt\\"> Pro ty, kte\\u0159\\u00ed je\\u0161t\\u011b nejsou obezn\\u00e1meni s touto situac\\u00ed, zde je stru\\u010dn\\u00fd popis ud\\u00e1losti. Hitpoint, jako partner <b>Riot Games</b>, byl pozv\\u00e1n do Berl\\u00edna, kde se konal sv\\u011btov\\u00fd \\u0161ampion\\u00e1t League of Legends. D\\u00edky \\u0159ad\\u011b \\u0161\\u0165astn\\u00fdch n\\u00e1hod se jim poda\\u0159ilo z\\u00edskat jednu z vys\\u00edlac\\u00edch bun\\u011bk p\\u0159\\u00edmo na stadi\\u00f3nu, odkud \\u017eiv\\u011b vys\\u00edlali vy\\u0159azovac\\u00ed z\\u00e1pasy. Toto byl zna\\u010dn\\u00fd \\u00fasp\\u011bch pro relativn\\u011b malou organizaci. Nicm\\u00e9n\\u011b b\\u011bhem jednoho z vys\\u00edl\\u00e1n\\u00ed, konkr\\u00e9tn\\u011b b\\u011bhem z\\u00e1pasu mezi evropsk\\u00fdm t\\u00fdmem <b>G2 Esport</b> a \\u010d\\u00ednsk\\u00fdm t\\u00fdmem <b>Bilibili Gaming</b>, do\\u0161lo k probl\\u00e9m\\u016fm. Koment\\u00e1\\u0159 <b>Hitpointu</b> b\\u011bhem tohoto z\\u00e1pasu byl nezvykle neobvykl\\u00fd. Zd\\u00e1lo se, \\u017ee koment\\u00e1to\\u0159i jsou pod vlivem alkoholu, ned\\u00e1vali pozor na d\\u011bn\\u00ed ve h\\u0159e a nep\\u0159ikl\\u00e1dali d\\u016fle\\u017eitost sv\\u00e9 roli. Nejhor\\u0161\\u00ed bylo, \\u017ee produkce nezas\\u00e1hla a nechala koment\\u00e1tory pokra\\u010dovat v tomto stavu po v\\u011bt\\u0161inu z\\u00e1pasu.</p><p data-block-key=\\"17ej9\\">Celou situaci ve\\u0159ejn\\u011b odsoudil b\\u00fdval\\u00fd koment\\u00e1tor s p\\u0159ezd\\u00edvkou <b>Davkouny</b> na sv\\u00e9m Youtube kan\\u00e1lu Riftczech, kde kritizoval nejen samotn\\u00e9 vys\\u00edl\\u00e1n\\u00ed, ale tak\\u00e9 upozornil na intern\\u00ed probl\\u00e9my organizace a jej\\u00ed p\\u0159\\u00edstup k fanou\\u0161k\\u016fm.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fju1XnPNYLU\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"ba7a0\\"></p>", "id": "6b85ec34-fce9-47e4-8de2-6566bda8d397"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"vkb9g\\">Vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159en\\u00ed, kter\\u00e9 situaci eskalovalo</h3><p data-block-key=\\"bgfe6\\">V reakci na tento incident vydala organizace <b>Hitpoint</b> \\u010dl\\u00e1nek na sv\\u00e9m webu, ve kter\\u00e9m se vyjad\\u0159ovala k cel\\u00e9 situaci. M\\u00edsto aby v\\u0161ak uklidnili sv\\u00e9 fanou\\u0161ky, sv\\u00fdm prohl\\u00e1\\u0161en\\u00edm komunitu sp\\u00ed\\u0161e rozl\\u00edtili. V\\u011bt\\u0161inu obvin\\u011bn\\u00ed pop\\u0159eli a cel\\u00fd ne\\u00fasp\\u011bch p\\u0159isoudili \\u00fanav\\u011b z n\\u00e1ro\\u010dn\\u00e9ho vys\\u00edl\\u00e1n\\u00ed, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e si p\\u0159itom v\\u00fdrazn\\u011b boostovali ego. Nav\\u00edc v\\u0161echny sv\\u00e9 kritiky ozna\\u010dili za lh\\u00e1\\u0159e, co\\u017e situaci je\\u0161t\\u011b zhor\\u0161ilo.</p><p data-block-key=\\"2bgtt\\">Toto jedn\\u00e1n\\u00ed vedlo k tomu, \\u017ee n\\u011bkolik intern\\u00edch koment\\u00e1tor\\u016f se rozhodlo ukon\\u010dit spolupr\\u00e1ci s organizac\\u00ed. Mezi nimi byl i obl\\u00edben\\u00fd koment\\u00e1tor Mortsche, kter\\u00fd po v\\u00edce ne\\u017e p\\u011bti letech spolupr\\u00e1ci ukon\\u010dil a na sv\\u00e9m <b>YouTube</b> kan\\u00e1le zve\\u0159ejnil vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159en\\u00ed, kde upozor\\u0148oval na dal\\u0161\\u00ed probl\\u00e9my v r\\u00e1mci organizace.</p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=niMk-Vhr50o\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"e8obf\\"></p>", "id": "40c396b1-c414-45fd-ab77-0148e1305a30"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "e9b1e0bc-9f40-4973-bae0-99af184ccbcc"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"vkb9g\\">Uzn\\u00e1n\\u00ed p\\u0159e\\u0161lapu a slib k lep\\u0161\\u00edmu fungov\\u00e1n\\u00ed</h3><p data-block-key=\\"8luet\\">Situace donutila <b>Hitpoint</b> p\\u0159ehodnotit sv\\u00e9 postupy a pr\\u00e1v\\u011b v\\u010dera organizace na sv\\u00e9m YouTube kan\\u00e1le zve\\u0159ejnila video, ve kter\\u00e9m majitel s p\\u0159ezd\\u00edvkou Smoke p\\u0159iznal chyby a omluvil se za nezda\\u0159en\\u00e9 vys\\u00edl\\u00e1n\\u00ed. Z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 sl\\u00edbil, \\u017ee se organizace bude sna\\u017eit zlep\\u0161it ve v\\u00edce oblastech. </p><p data-block-key=\\"81od0\\">Div\\u00e1k\\u016fm byl nab\\u00eddnut formul\\u00e1\\u0159, aby mohli vyj\\u00e1d\\u0159it sv\\u00e9 n\\u00e1zory a n\\u00e1pady na zlep\\u0161en\\u00ed fungov\\u00e1n\\u00ed organizace. Reakce na omluvu se r\\u016fznily, n\\u011bkte\\u0159\\u00ed byli spokojen\\u00ed, jin\\u00ed st\\u00e1le nejsou pln\\u011b p\\u0159esv\\u011bd\\u010deni o up\\u0159\\u00edmnosti Hitpointu k prov\\u00e1d\\u011bn\\u00ed zm\\u011bn, co\\u017e je pochopiteln\\u00e9. Jsem zv\\u011bdav\\u00fd, zda Hitpoint dodr\\u017e\\u00ed sv\\u00e9 sliby. Zd\\u00e1 se, \\u017ee kauza by mohla b\\u00fdt u konce, co\\u017e by bylo v\\u00edtan\\u00e9, vzhledem k tomu, \\u017ee \\u010desk\\u00e1 sc\\u00e9na <b>League of Legends</b> e-sportu v posledn\\u00ed dob\\u011b stagnuje. </p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZvPeW0iMGr0\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"45i8n\\"><b>Co si o t\\u00e9to kauze mysl\\u00edte vy? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt n\\u00ed\\u017ee do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f</b></p>", "id": "6e462f0b-3c64-4112-9c3b-ee461fac96a4"}]	62	145	league of legends, hitpoint, esko, kauze, cz	\N	0	2	0
