62	Srpen nm pomalu kon a zijov nabdka her Xbox Game Pass se pomalu rsuje. Z se hlavn ponese hlavn ve znamen strategi.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"25jt3\\"><b>A\\u0165 u\\u017e jste fanou\\u0161ky historick\\u00fdch ta\\u017een\\u00ed, mytologie, nebo budovatelsk\\u00fdch strategi\\u00ed, z\\u00e1\\u0159ijov\\u00e1 nab\\u00eddka Game Passu v\\u00e1s rozhodn\\u011b nenech\\u00e1 chladn\\u00fdmi. Teda nech\\u00e1 v p\\u0159\\u00edpad\\u011b Frostpunk 2.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"9sdub\\"><b>Z\\u00e1\\u0159ijov\\u00e1 nab\\u00eddka na Game Passu</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"ot9v\\">Opalovac\\u00ed kr\\u00e9m a plavky m\\u016f\\u017eou zp\\u00e1tky do sk\\u0159\\u00edn\\u011b, proto\\u017ee s p\\u0159\\u00edchodem z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed se hern\\u00ed sv\\u011bt probouz\\u00ed op\\u011bt k \\u017eivotu. Pokud jste p\\u0159edplatitel\\u00e9 <b>Game Passu</b> a z\\u00e1rove\\u0148 fanou\\u0161ci strategi\\u00ed, z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed se v\\u00e1m bude opravdu l\\u00edbit.</p><p data-block-key=\\"2eu3o\\">Ji\\u017e 4. z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed se m\\u016f\\u017eete t\\u011b\\u0161it na epick\\u00fd n\\u00e1vrat legend\\u00e1rn\\u00ed strategie <b>Age of Mythology: Retold</b>. Sta\\u010d\\u00ed opr\\u00e1\\u0161it znalosti starov\\u011bk\\u00e9 mytologie a hur\\u00e1 do toho. A pokud jste nedo\\u010dkav\\u00ed, m\\u016f\\u017eete si hru u\\u017e te\\u010f p\\u0159edinstalovat.</p><p data-block-key=\\"coj9f\\">Ani druh\\u00e1 polovina z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed nez\\u016fstane pozadu. 20. z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed se toti\\u017e m\\u016f\\u017eete vydat do mraziv\\u00e9ho sv\\u011bta ve h\\u0159e <b>Frostpunk 2</b>. Sv\\u011bt je sice na pokraji zk\\u00e1zy, ale vy m\\u00e1te \\u0161anci ho zachr\\u00e1nit.  Hra byla p\\u016fvodn\\u011b pl\\u00e1nov\\u00e1na na d\\u0159\\u00edv\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed datum, ale v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i se rozhodli pro odklad, aby mohli hru je\\u0161t\\u011b v\\u00edce doladit a poskytnout hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm co nejlep\\u0161\\u00ed z\\u00e1\\u017eitek.</p>", "id": "6f6202e4-f19a-401a-82cf-69c67b96729e"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "4a59b4a9-aa3a-4069-bbfa-8fc53fb564e3"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"25jt3\\">A jako t\\u0159e\\u0161ni\\u010dku na dortu tu m\\u00e1me <b>Ara: History Untold</b>. Dal\\u0161\\u00ed z \\u0159ady velk\\u00fdch strategi\\u00ed v\\u00e1s provede d\\u011bjinami lidstva a umo\\u017en\\u00ed v\\u00e1m p\\u0159epsat jeho osud. Tak\\u017ee pokud jste v\\u017edycky snili o tom, st\\u00e1t se vl\\u00e1dcem sv\\u011bta, te\\u010f m\\u00e1te \\u0161anci! </p><p data-block-key=\\"43ulo\\"><b>Na kterou z v\\u00fd\\u0161e uveden\\u00fdch her se t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edte nejv\\u00edce? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f nebo na na\\u0161e soci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed s\\u00edt\\u011b. Nezapome\\u0148te se pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 na na\\u0161e ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e9 video, kde se v\\u011bnujeme strategi\\u00edm od Paradoxu.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u6apwkol1j0&amp;t\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"a5p15\\"></p>", "id": "457f8e6e-288a-4218-a6a7-b7b86d601d7c"}]	127	28	z, xbox, xbox game pass, strategie, ara: history untold, age of mythology, frostpunk 2	\N	0	0	0
116	Akcie Ubisoftu opt vrazn klesly, protoe jeden z vznamnch meninovch akcion tla na to, aby spolenost pela do soukromch rukou	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"7ouc0\\"><b>Ubisoft se nad\\u00e1le pot\\u00fdk\\u00e1 s poklesem akci\\u00ed a rostouc\\u00ed nejistotou mezi akcion\\u00e1\\u0159i. Po slab\\u00fdch prodej\\u00edch her, jako je Star Wars: Outlaws, a propadu hr\\u00e1\\u010dsk\\u00fdch \\u010d\\u00edsel u XDefiantu se akcie Ubisoftu ocitly na desetilet\\u00e9m minimu.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"a5nna\\"><b>Akcie Ubisoftu klesaj\\u00ed</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"dns5j\\">Akcie <b>Ubisoftu</b> klesly v dob\\u011b psan\\u00ed \\u010dl\\u00e1nku o v\\u00edce ne\\u017e <b>7 %</b>, \\u010d\\u00edm\\u017e se situace spole\\u010dnosti dostala do je\\u0161t\\u011b v\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00edho nap\\u011bt\\u00ed. V dob\\u011b psan\\u00ed \\u010dl\\u00e1nku se tak cena akci\\u00ed pohybuje okolo 13,66 USD dle TradingView. </p><p data-block-key=\\"c9c5m\\">P\\u00e1d n\\u00e1sledoval po tlaku od jednoho z <b>v\\u00fdznamn\\u00fdch men\\u0161inov\\u00fdch akcion\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f</b>, kter\\u00fd po\\u017eaduje, aby Ubisoft p\\u0159e\\u0161el do <b>soukrom\\u00fdch rukou</b>. Minul\\u00fd t\\u00fdden tak\\u00e9 do\\u0161lo k poklesu akci\\u00ed po zpr\\u00e1v\\u00e1ch, \\u017ee <b>XDefiant</b> ztr\\u00e1c\\u00ed hr\\u00e1\\u010de. Situace byla je\\u0161t\\u011b umocn\\u011bna vla\\u017en\\u00fdm p\\u0159ijet\\u00edm hry <b>Star Wars: Outlaws</b>, co\\u017e vedlo k tomu, \\u017ee cena akci\\u00ed Ubisoftu klesla na nejni\\u017e\\u0161\\u00ed hodnotu za posledn\\u00edch <b>10 let</b>.</p>", "id": "8984ab62-c08e-4c81-ba17-9b6efb26128c"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "28b69d4d-373d-4e44-b558-b92090c478d7"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"7ouc0\\">Ani posledn\\u00ed tituly nep\\u0159inesly k\\u00fd\\u017een\\u00fd obrat. Vezm\\u011bme si nap\\u0159\\u00edklad Skull &amp; Bones \\u010di Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora