122	Slavn skateboardista Tony Hawk v nedvnm podcastu prozradil, e spolen s Activisionam pracuje na nem k 25 vro srie Tony Hawk's Pro Skater.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"2krtb\\"><b>Slavn\\u00fd skateboardista Tony Hawk v ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e9m podcastu prozradil, \\u017ee spole\\u010dn\\u011b s Activisionam pracuje na n\\u011b\\u010dem k 25 v\\u00fdro\\u010d\\u00ed s\\u00e9rie Tony Hawk's Pro Skater.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"b7o1h\\"><b>\\"Na n\\u011b\\u010dem s Activisionem pracujeme\\" prozradil Tony Hawk v ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e9m podcastu</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"22o56\\"><b>Tony Hawk's Pro Skater </b>je skateboardov\\u00e1 ark\\u00e1dov\\u00e1 s\\u00e9rie, kter\\u00e1 se nejv\\u00edce proslavila pr\\u00e1v\\u011b na konzoli <b>Playstation 2</b> a dodnes je pova\\u017eov\\u00e1na za jednu z lep\\u0161\\u00edch skateboardov\\u00fdch her na trhu. Ale posledn\\u00ed hra z t\\u00e9to s\\u00e9rie vy\\u0161la v roce 2020, kdy jsme jako hr\\u00e1\\u010di dostali <b>remaster prvn\\u00edch 2 d\\u00edl\\u016f</b> v jednom titulu. Av\\u0161ak zd\\u00e1 se, \\u017ee na <b>25. v\\u00fdro\\u010d\\u00ed</b> t\\u00e9to s\\u00e9rie bude Activision n\\u011bco p\\u0159ipravovat. </p>", "id": "a53d2e36-0a29-4267-829b-af3d18c67aaa"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "1164dac7-905a-40d6-b44a-0d1a2f248d5b"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"2krtb\\">Obnoven\\u00ed spolupr\\u00e1ce</h3><p data-block-key=\\"f2ffc\\">Zat\\u00edm nev\\u00edme \\u00fapln\\u011b s jistotou, co p\\u0159esn\\u011b spole\\u010dnost <b>Activision</b> k v\\u00fdro\\u010d\\u00ed s\\u00e9rie chyst\\u00e1, ale jedno v\\u00edme se stoprocentn\\u00ed jistotou. Samotn\\u00fd legend\\u00e1rn\\u00ed skater <b>Tony Hawk</b> znovu za\\u010dal komunikovat se spole\\u010dnost\\u00ed a dokonce s nimi spolupracovat. Tuto informaci potvrdil v podcastu <b>Mythical Kitchen</b> kde Hawk \\u0159ekl: <b><i>\\u201eP\\u0159\\u00e1l bych si, abych v\\u00e1m mohl \\u0159\\u00edct v\\u00edc, ale jedin\\u00e9, co mohu prozradit, je op\\u011btovn\\u00e1 komunikace s Activisionem, se kter\\u00fdm na n\\u011b\\u010dem pracujeme\\". </i></b>K tomu je\\u0161te Hawk dodal, \\u017ee to na \\u010dem s Activisionem pracuje by m\\u011blo hr\\u00e1\\u010de s\\u00e9rie pot\\u011b\\u0161it. Bohu\\u017eel v\\u00edce informac\\u00ed jsme nedostali.</p>", "id": "5ec84ba5-1ba6-4487-b038-fcd0bcac7884"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"2krtb\\">P\\u0159\\u00edpravy a spekulace</h3><p data-block-key=\\"f93vk\\">A nyn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i se pomalu p\\u0159ipravuj\\u00ed na toto <b>25. v\\u00fdro\\u010d\\u00ed</b> t\\u00e9to legend\\u00e1rn\\u00ed s\\u00e9rie. Tomu odpov\\u00edd\\u00e1 i \\u00fa\\u010det s\\u00e9rie na soci\\u00e1ln\\u00ed s\\u00e9rii <a href=\\"https://x.com/tonyhawkthegame?lang=en\\"><b>X (Twitter)</b></a>, kde hlavn\\u00ed banner a logo je zm\\u011bn\\u011bno k v\\u00fdro\\u010d\\u00ed s\\u00e9rie. A pozorn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed fanou\\u0161ci poznamenali, \\u017ee tyto bannery jsou <b>upraven\\u00e9 artworky</b>, kter\\u00e9 doprov\\u00e1zeli p\\u0159ed\\u011bl\\u00e1vky prvn\\u00edch dvou d\\u00edl\\u016f v kolekci <b>Ton Hawk's Pro Skater 1+2</b> a tak n\\u011bkte\\u0159\\u00ed se domn\\u00edvali, \\u017ee se chystaj\\u00ed p\\u0159ed\\u011bl\\u00e1vky t\\u0159et\\u00edho a \\u010dtvrt\\u00e9ho d\\u00edlu. A v minulosti se na t\\u011bchto remac\\u00edch i pracovalo, ale bohu\\u017eel studio kter\\u00e9 na nich d\\u011blalo spadlo do struktur <b>Blizzardu</b> a t\\u00edm v\\u00fdvoj skon\\u010dil v propadli\\u0161ti d\\u011bjin. Ale uvid\\u00edme co <b>29. z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed</b>, kdy je ofici\\u00e1ln\\u00ed den 25. v\\u00fdro\\u010d\\u00ed s\\u00e9rie, Activision p\\u0159edstav\\u00ed.</p>", "id": "f45def7c-1b74-4246-83ce-8d376672fa65"}]	0	89		\N	0	0	0
110	Astro Bot je podle vech dostupnch recenz nejlep hrou tohoto msce, a Sony si je vdoma, e hri chtj vce obsahu. Vypad to, e jejich pn bude brzy vyslyeno.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"l6l9d\\"><b>Astro Bot je dle v\\u0161ech hodnocen\\u00ed zat\\u00edm nejlep\\u0161\\u00ed hrou tohoto m\\u011bs\\u00edce a Sony si uv\\u011bdomuje, \\u017ee hr\\u00e1\\u010di tou\\u017e\\u00ed po dal\\u0161\\u00edm obsahu. A zd\\u00e1 se, \\u017ee tomu tak skute\\u010dn\\u011b bude.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"460d1\\"><b>Dal\\u0161\\u00ed pl\\u00e1ny pro hru Astro Bot</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"5o35j\\">Studio <b>Team Asobi</b> a spole\\u010dnost <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"107\\"><b>Sony</b></a> zaznamenaly se hrou Astro Bot obrovsk\\u00fd \\u00fasp\\u011bch, z\\u00edskaly skv\\u011bl\\u00e9 hodnocen\\u00ed jak od kritik\\u016f, tak od hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, a stala se nejlep\\u0161\\u00ed hrou tohoto m\\u011bs\\u00edce, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e n\\u011bkte\\u0159\\u00ed tvrd\\u00ed, \\u017ee i cel\\u00e9ho roku. V\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i si jsou tohoto \\u00fasp\\u011bchu v\\u011bdomi a pl\\u00e1nuj\\u00ed roz\\u0161\\u00ed\\u0159en\\u00ed hry o dal\\u0161\\u00ed obsah. Co v\\u0161echno bude p\\u0159id\\u00e1no, z\\u016fst\\u00e1v\\u00e1 zat\\u00edm ot\\u00e1zkou. </p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6iJqC0hfX6w\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"54cig\\"></p>", "id": "d44d3dad-331b-406b-9997-99da8bb29d54"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "4830d216-7160-44d3-b2ac-b93a0bffd5eb"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"l6l9d\\">Pl\\u00e1ny do budoucna</h3><p data-block-key=\\"8kfk0\\">Nicolas Doucet, \\u0161\\u00e9f studia Team Asobi, poskytl informace o nadch\\u00e1zej\\u00edc\\u00edm rozvoji hry <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"106\\"><b>Astro Bot</b></a>. Podle jeho slov se hr\\u00e1\\u010di mohou t\\u011b\\u0161it na bezplatn\\u00e9 DLC, kter\\u00e9 by m\\u011blo p\\u0159in\\u00e9st asi 10 nov\\u00f