184	Hern prmysl se u dlouhodob posouv smrem k digitlnm prodejm, ale nov daje za rok 2024 ukazuj, e tento trend zesiluje.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"ktefv\\"><b>I kdy\\u017e fyzick\\u00e9 kopie st\\u00e1le hraj\\u00ed svou roli, zvl\\u00e1\\u0161t\\u011b na platform\\u00e1ch jako je Nintendo Switch, v\\u011bt\\u0161ina her se nyn\\u00ed prod\\u00e1v\\u00e1 digit\\u00e1ln\\u011b, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e PlayStation a Xbox vid\\u00ed v\\u00fdrazn\\u00fd pokles fyzick\\u00fdch prodej\\u016f.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"9cefv\\"><b>P\\u0159echod k digit\\u00e1ln\\u00edm produkt\\u016fm</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"2vatl\\">Posun k digit\\u00e1lu je nejz\\u0159eteln\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed na <b>PlayStationu</b> a <b>Xboxu</b>. V roce <b>2023</b> se nap\\u0159\\u00edklad <b>41 % nov\\u00fdch her</b> na <b>PS5</b> prodalo fyzicky, ale v roce <b>2024</b> tento pod\\u00edl klesl na <b>32 %</b>. Na <b>Xboxu</b> se fyzick\\u00e9 prodeje sn\\u00ed\\u017eily je\\u0161t\\u011b v\\u00fdrazn\\u011bji. V roce <b>2023</b> bylo fyzicky prod\\u00e1no <b>26 %</b> her pro <b>Xbox Series S a X</b>, ale letos u\\u017e jen <b>19 %</b>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"nbtc\\">Jinak je tomu u <b>Nintendo Switch</b>, kde fyzick\\u00e9 kopie st\\u00e1le dominuj\\u00ed. Pro t\\u0159et\\u00ed strany na <b>Switchi</b> se 65 % nov\\u00fdch her prodalo fyzicky. I kdy\\u017e to p\\u0159edstavuje pokles oproti lo\\u0148sk\\u00fdm <b>67 %</b>, platforma st\\u00e1le odol\\u00e1v\\u00e1 tlaku na digitalizaci, p\\u0159edev\\u0161\\u00edm d\\u00edky sv\\u00e9 c\\u00edlov\\u00e9 skupin\\u011b.</p><h3 data-block-key=\\"ahlga\\">Zm\\u011bny v preferenc\\u00edch prodeje podle \\u017e\\u00e1nru</h3><p data-block-key=\\"3hve9\\">Zaj\\u00edmav\\u00e9 je, \\u017ee digitalizace nen\\u00ed stejn\\u00e1 pro v\\u0161echny typy her. Nap\\u0159\\u00edklad <b>multiplayerov\\u00e9 st\\u0159\\u00edle\\u010dky</b> se prod\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed z v\\u011bt\\u0161\\u00ed \\u010d\\u00e1sti digit\\u00e1ln\\u011b, kde n\\u011bkdy a\\u017e <b>90 %</b> prodej\\u016f prob\\u00edh\\u00e1 online. Na druhou stranu <b>singleplayerov\\u00e9 hry</b> nebo <b>podobn\\u00e9 tituly</b> \\u010dasto dosahuj\\u00ed lep\\u0161\\u00edch v\\u00fdsledk\\u016f u fyzick\\u00fdch prodejc\\u016f. To bylo vid\\u011bt nap\\u0159\\u00edklad u <b>Hogwarts Legacy</b> v roce <b>2023</b>, co\\u017e byla hra, kter\\u00e1 p\\u0159it\\u00e1hla \\u0161irokou \\u0161k\\u00e1lu hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, a velk\\u00e1 \\u010d\\u00e1st prodej\\u016f prob\\u011bhla fyzicky. Letos v\\u0161ak podobn\\u00fd masivn\\u00ed mainstreamov\\u00fd titul chyb\\u00ed, co\\u017e je jeden z d\\u016fvod\\u016f, pro\\u010d se trh v\\u00edce p\\u0159iklonil k digit\\u00e1ln\\u00edm prodej\\u016fm.</p>", "id": "651ba9fe-e9f8-4233-a53e-ebf3c0ce4a9f"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "0f6fb2c7-5d96-456f-bad7-059e6b07e80c"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\\"ktefv\\">Sportovn\\u00ed hry a ro\\u010dn\\u00ed aktualizace</h3><p data-block-key=\\"78ve6\\">Dal\\u0161\\u00ed zaj\\u00edmav\\u00fd ukazatel digit\\u00e1ln\\u00edho r\\u016fstu p\\u0159edstavuj\\u00ed <b>sportovn\\u00ed tituly</b>, jako je <b>EA Sports FC 25</b>, <b>NBA 2K25</b> nebo <b>WWE 2K24</b>. Zde jsme tak\\u00e9 zaznamenali n\\u00e1r\\u016fst digit\\u00e1ln\\u00edch prodej\\u016f, by\\u0165 ne tak dramatick\\u00fd jako u jin\\u00fdch her. U n\\u011bkter\\u00fdch titul\\u016f se digit\\u00e1ln\\u00ed pod\\u00edl zv\\u00fd\\u0161il jen o <b>1 % a\\u017e 2 %</b>, zat\\u00edmco u jin\\u00fdch se posunul a\\u017e o <b>5 %</b>.</p><h3 data-block-key=\\"cuu5f\\">Fyzick\\u00fd trh z\\u016fst\\u00e1v\\u00e1 relevantn\\u00ed</h3><p data-block-key=\\"2r4rj\\">Navzdory zvy\\u0161uj\\u00edc\\u00ed se popularit\\u011b digit\\u00e1ln\\u00edch prodej\\u016f si fyzick\\u00fd trh st\\u00e1le dr\\u017e\\u00ed sv\\u00e9 m\\u00edsto. V prvn\\u00edch dev\\u00edti m\\u011bs\\u00edc\\u00edch roku <b>2024</b> se v Evrop\\u011b prodalo <b>32 milion\\u016f fyzick\\u