95	Discord, oblben komunikan platforma mezi hri, pedstavila novou verzi svho klienta, kter umouje vaim ptelm vidt vai kompletn hern historii.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"kqv06\\"><b>Hran\\u00ed her se stalo spole\\u010denskou aktivitou a Discord je centrem t\\u00e9to komunity. Nov\\u00e1 verze klienta v\\u0161ak odhaluje va\\u0161i hern\\u00ed historii p\\u0159\\u00e1tel\\u016fm.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"fki8a\\"><b>Discord op\\u011bt roz\\u0161i\\u0159uje sv\\u00e9 hern\\u00ed funkce</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"da62t\\">S novou verz\\u00ed <b>Discordu </b>p\\u0159ich\\u00e1z\\u00ed funkce, kter\\u00e1 umo\\u017e\\u0148uje va\\u0161im p\\u0159\\u00e1tel\\u016fm vid\\u011bt nejen to, jakou hru pr\\u00e1v\\u011b hrajete, ale tak\\u00e9 va\\u0161i kompletn\\u00ed hern\\u00ed historii, v\\u010detn\\u011b \\u010dasu str\\u00e1ven\\u00e9ho u jednotliv\\u00fdch titul\\u016f. Zm\\u011bna znamen\\u00e1, \\u017ee po\\u010det hodin, kter\\u00e9 jste str\\u00e1vili ve h\\u0159e, je nyn\\u00ed pln\\u011b viditeln\\u00fd va\\u0161im p\\u0159\\u00e1tel\\u016fm na <b>Discordu</b>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"fg9rn\\">Nov\\u00e1 funkce je jako dvouse\\u010dn\\u00e1 zbra\\u0148. Na jedn\\u00e9 stran\\u011b otev\\u00edr\\u00e1 dve\\u0159e do sv\\u011bta spole\\u010dn\\u00e9ho hran\\u00ed, kde va\\u0161i kamar\\u00e1di kone\\u010dn\\u011b uvid\\u00ed, co pr\\u00e1v\\u011b pa\\u0159\\u00edte, a mohou se k v\\u00e1m kdykoliv p\\u0159idat. Je to jako hern\\u00ed seznamka, kter\\u00e1 v\\u00e1s propoj\\u00ed s podobn\\u011b nalad\\u011bn\\u00fdmi hr\\u00e1\\u010di a inspiruje k objevov\\u00e1n\\u00ed nov\\u00fdch hern\\u00edch sv\\u011bt\\u016f.</p>", "id": "e5c8135f-e59f-407e-9000-d176eec3bef3"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "05030b95-486e-4e4b-9fde-1c32414efbf7"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"kqv06\\">Na druh\\u00e9 stran\\u011b se oz\\u00fdvaj\\u00ed hlasy, kter\\u00e9 se ob\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed o sv\\u00e9 soukrom\\u00ed. Pro n\\u011bkter\\u00e9 je sd\\u00edlen\\u00ed hern\\u00edch n\\u00e1vyk\\u016f jako odhalov\\u00e1n\\u00ed tajn\\u00e9ho den\\u00edku. M\\u016f\\u017ee to v\\u00e9st k nep\\u0159\\u00edjemn\\u00e9mu tlaku na hran\\u00ed ur\\u010dit\\u00fdch her nebo k pocitu, \\u017ee je n\\u011bkdo neust\\u00e1le sleduje. Je to jako m\\u00edt <b>Velk\\u00e9ho bratra</b>, kter\\u00fd v\\u00e1m kouk\\u00e1 p\\u0159es rameno, kdy\\u017e si chcete jen tak zahr\\u00e1t.</p>", "id": "6e4f9b41-7859-4b86-b598-5f7d87e5ebfe"}]	37	60	discord, gaming, hry	\N	1	3	0
100	Spolenost PlayStation oznmila, e po pouhch dvou tdnech od vydn ukonuje provoz sv nov hry Concord.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"oazzz\\"><b>Concord, nov\\u00fd titul od PlayStation, nep\\u0159inesl o\\u010dek\\u00e1van\\u00fd \\u00fasp\\u011bch. Kv\\u016fli slab\\u00e9 odezv\\u011b hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f se PlayStation rozhodl hru st\\u00e1hnout a vr\\u00e1tit pen\\u00edze.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"76um2\\"><b>Concord kon\\u010d\\u00ed</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"dfha6\\">Hero-shooter st\\u0159\\u00edle\\u010dka <b>Concord</b>, vydan\\u00e1 23. srpna, bohu\\u017eel nesplnila o\\u010dek\\u00e1v\\u00e1n\\u00ed. V den vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed dos\\u00e1hla na platform\\u011b <b>Steam</b> m\\u00e9n\\u011b ne\\u017e 700 soub\\u011b\\u017en\\u00fdch hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e toto \\u010d\\u00edslo b\\u011bhem n\\u00e1sleduj\\u00edc\\u00edch dn\\u00ed d\\u00e1le klesalo. V dob\\u011b psan\\u00ed \\u010dl\\u00e1nku dokonce po\\u010det hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f dos\\u00e1hl 40, p\\u0159i\\u010dem\\u017e denn\\u00ed maximum dos\\u00e1hlo 134.</p><p data-block-key=\\"1d87\\">Odhady nazna\\u010duj\\u00ed, \\u017ee na konzoli PlayStation 5 se prodalo p\\u0159ibli\\u017en\\u011b 25 000 kopi\\u00ed, av\\u0161ak po zohledn\\u011bn\\u00ed vr\\u00e1cen\\u00ed pen\\u011bz je skute\\u010dn\\u00fd po\\u010det pravd\\u011bpodobn\\u011b ni\\u017e\\u0161\\u00ed. I p\\u0159es zna\\u010dn\\u00e9 investice a o\\u010dek\\u00e1v\\u00e1n\\u00ed se PlayStation rozhodl ukon\\u010dit provoz hry 6. z\\u00e1\\u0159\\u00ed a hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016fm nab\\u00eddnout plnou finan\\u010dn\\u00ed n\\u00e1hradu. Ne\\u00fasp\\u011bch Concordu je nepochybn\\u011b pro <a linktype=\\"page\\" id=\\"97\\"><b>PlayStation</b></a> velk\\u00fdm zklam\\u00e1n\\u00edm.</p>", "id": "f788bfdd-6aa2-4750-b2d1-db6377503437"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "66e30051-6433-415e-9827-4955efb12e14"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"oazzz\\">Co