157	Tento msc nabdne PlayStation Plus fanoukm adu skvlch hernch zitk, vetn hororovho remaku Dead Space, psychologickho thrilleru Doki Doki Literature Club Plus a zpasnick akce WWE 2K24.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"l6ybu\\"><b>\\u0158\\u00edjnov\\u00e1 nab\\u00eddka her pro PlayStation Plus nab\\u00edz\\u00ed pom\\u011brn\\u011b slu\\u0161nou d\\u00e1vku z\\u00e1bavy, od vesm\\u00edrn\\u00e9ho hororu Dead Space a\\u017e po z\\u00e1pasy ve h\\u0159e WWE 2K24. </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"bhlqf\\"><b>PlayStation Plus na \\u0159\\u00edjen</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"dbpji\\">\\u0158\\u00edjnov\\u00e1 nab\\u00eddka her zdarma pro <b>PlayStation Plus</b> p\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed t\\u0159i tituly, kter\\u00e9 jsou k dispozici ji\\u017e nyn\\u00ed. Hr\\u00e1\\u010di, kte\\u0159\\u00ed maj\\u00ed p\\u0159edplatn\\u00e9 <b>Essential</b>, <b>Extra</b> nebo <b>Premium</b>, mohou stahovat tyto hry po celou dobu jejich dostupnosti. </p><p data-block-key=\\"feqq6\\">Prvn\\u00ed na \\u0159ad\\u011b je <b>Dead Space</b> remake kultovn\\u00ed hororov\\u00e9 hry.  <b>Dead Space</b> je exkluzivn\\u011b dostupn\\u00fd pro <b>PS5</b>, co\\u017e znamen\\u00e1, \\u017ee hr\\u00e1\\u010di na star\\u0161\\u00edch konzol\\u00edch si ho neu\\u017eij\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"d7fqu\\">Dal\\u0161\\u00ed na seznamu je <b>Doki Doki Literature Club Plus</b>, hra, kter\\u00e1 na prvn\\u00ed pohled p\\u016fsob\\u00ed jako nevinn\\u00e1 vizu\\u00e1ln\\u00ed novela, ale ve skute\\u010dnosti nab\\u00edz\\u00ed mnohem v\\u00edce. Titul je dostupn\\u00fd jak na <b>PS4</b>, tak na <b>PS5.</b></p>", "id": "b9068656-976d-41a2-a45d-b63f834f7b5b"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "084876f9-c584-43f6-9f19-afaffe6bd1db"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"l6ybu\\">A kone\\u010dn\\u011b, posledn\\u00ed na seznamu tu m\\u00e1me <b>WWE 2K24</b>. Hra je dostupn\\u00e1 pro ob\\u011b generace konzol\\u00ed. Pokud m\\u00e1te chu\\u0165 se pustit d