145	Fortnite oznmil nov hern md s nzvem Ranked Reload, kter bude k dispozici ode dneka. Tento nov reim pin monosti hran s povolenm stavnm i bez nj.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"qiz6s\\"><b>Fortnite roz\\u0161i\\u0159uje svou nab\\u00eddku hern\\u00edch m\\u00f3d\\u016f o nov\\u00fd re\\u017eim nazvan\\u00fd Ranked Reload.</b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"8gme2\\"><b>Ranked Reload doraz\\u00ed ji\\u017e dnes</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"3e5nv\\">Nov\\u00fd re\\u017eim, kter\\u00fd doraz\\u00ed ji\\u017e dnes, p\\u0159ich\\u00e1z\\u00ed s mo\\u017enost\\u00ed volby mezi klasick\\u00fdm stav\\u011bn\\u00edm a <b>Zero Build</b> m\\u00f3dem. M\\u00f3d bude podporovat pouze t\\u00fdmy slo\\u017een\\u00e9 ze dvou nebo v\\u00edce hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f.</p><p data-block-key=\\"8hi0e\\">Nav\\u00edc, hr\\u00e1\\u010di se mohou t\\u011b\\u0161it na exkluzivn\\u00ed skin, kter\\u00fd obdr\\u017e\\u00ed zdarma jako sou\\u010d\\u00e1st t\\u00e9to aktualizace.</p>", "id": "2c3d0fd6-7a0a-4676-abb3-d17611b1f599"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "1163d69f-ad6a-41d5-b676-42ed0646678e"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"qiz6s\\"><b>Reload </b>je ve hr\\u00e1ch obl\\u00edben\\u00fd d\\u00edky sv\\u00e9mu rychl\\u00e9mu tempu a mo\\u017enosti o\\u017eiven\\u00ed t\\u00fdmov\\u00fdch hr\\u00e1\\u010d\\u016f, pokud jeden \\u010dlen st\\u00e1le p\\u0159e\\u017e\\u00edv\\u00e1. Nicm\\u00e9n\\u011b, jakmile se z\\u00e1pas bl\\u00ed\\u017e\\u00ed ke konci, mo\\u017enost o\\u017eiven\\u00ed miz\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"81e8k\\">Za\\u0159azen\\u00ed hodnocen\\u00e9ho m\\u00f3du do tohoto re\\u017eimu p\\u0159in\\u00e1\\u0161\\u00ed novou v\\u00fdzvu a p\\u0159\\u00edle\\u017eitost pro hr\\u00e1\\u010de uk\\u00e1zat sv\\u00e9 schopnosti v konkurenci s t\\u011bmi nejlep\\u0161\\u00edmi. </p><p data-block-key=\\"9a2vt\\">Ned\\u00e1vno jsme v\\u00e1s informovali o nov\\u00e9m eventu v podob\\u011b <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/