177	GSC Game World, vvoji Stalker 2: Heart of Chornobyl, potvrdili, e hra pi svm vydn pob na Xbox Series S pouze pi 30 FPS.	[{"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"ta20h\\"><b>A\\u010dkoliv bude Stalker 2 na Xbox Series S omezen na 30 FPS, v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i pracuj\\u00ed na tom, aby hra b\\u011b\\u017eela plynuleji. </b></p><h2 data-block-key=\\"2fkhi\\"><b>Datum vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed Stalker 2: Heart of Chornobyl se bl\\u00ed\\u017e\\u00ed</b></h2><p data-block-key=\\"e58qf\\">Fanou\\u0161ci s\\u00e9rie <b>Stalker</b> \\u010dekaj\\u00edc\\u00ed na vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-ma-byt-technologicky-zazrak-na-xboxu-pojede-na-60-fps\\"><b>Stalker 2: Heart of Chornobyl</b> </a>na <b>Xbox Series S</b> mohou po\\u010d\\u00edtat s t\\u00edm, \\u017ee hra pob\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed na t\\u00e9to platform\\u011b p\\u0159i <b>30 FPS</b>. V ned\\u00e1vn\\u00e9m rozhovoru pro <b>Windows Central</b> v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i z <b>GSC Game World</b> potvrdili, \\u017ee p\\u0159i vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed bude verze pro <b>Series S</b> omezena na <b>30 sn\\u00edmk\\u016f za sekundu</b>, zat\\u00edmco na v\\u00fdkonn\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed <b>Xbox Series X</b> hra b\\u011b\\u017e\\u00ed p\\u0159i <b>60 FPS</b>, i kdy\\u017e v n\\u011bkter\\u00fdch momentech m\\u016f\\u017ee doj\\u00edt k poklesu na <b>55 FPS</b>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"d352o\\">Tv\\u016frci hry nicm\\u00e9n\\u011b uvedli, \\u017ee pracuj\\u00ed na <b>performance m\\u00f3du</b> pro <b>Series S</b>, kter\\u00fd by umo\\u017enil dos\\u00e1hnout <b>60 FPS</b> i na t\\u00e9to platform\\u011b. <b>GSC Game World</b> zmi\\u0148uje, \\u017ee v\\u011b\\u0159\\u00ed, \\u017ee to je technicky mo\\u017en\\u00e9, i kdy\\u017e p\\u0159izn\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed, \\u017ee optimalizace na <b>Xbox Series S</b> byla velmi n\\u00e1ro\\u010dn\\u00e1. Na za\\u010d\\u00e1tku v\\u00fdvoje si v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i mysleli, \\u017ee bude <b><i>\\"nemo\\u017en\\u00e9\\"</i></b> hru na tuto platformu v\\u016fbec dostat kv\\u016fli slo\\u017eit\\u00fdm mechanik\\u00e1m a velk\\u00e9mu mno\\u017estv\\u00ed obsahu.</p>", "id": "df3fb855-1034-45dd-b6c9-ce984ee02a68"}, {"type": "advertisement", "value": {}, "id": "cfa8c48d-d316-4ca8-bef6-8ac644e5c573"}, {"type": "paragraph", "value": "<p data-block-key=\\"ta20h\\">Nicm\\u00e9n\\u011b po optimalizaci, kdy vyu\\u017eili vlastnosti <b>Unreal Engine</b> k efektivn\\u00edmu streamov\\u00e1n\\u00ed dat a <i>\\u201evyt\\u00e1hli ka\\u017ed\\u00fd megabajt z ka\\u017ed\\u00e9ho kousku syst\\u00e9mov\\u00e9ho obsahu\\u201c</i>, za\\u010dala b\\u00fdt verze pro <b>Xbox Series S</b> re\\u00e1ln\\u011bj\\u0161\\u00ed.</p><p data-block-key=\\"b43io\\">V\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159i poznamenali, \\u017ee jejich optimalizace ukazuje, \\u017ee i slo\\u017eit\\u00e9 hry mohou dos\\u00e1hnout <b>pam\\u011b\\u0165ov\\u00fdch limit\\u016f</b> t\\u00e9to platformy, i kdy\\u017e uzn\\u00e1vaj\\u00ed, \\u017ee ne ka\\u017ed\\u00fd v\\u00fdvoj\\u00e1\\u0159 m\\u00e1 \\u010das a prost\\u0159edky na podobn\\u00e9 \\u00fapravy.</p><p data-block-key=\\"7iag1\\"><b>Stalker 2: Heart of Chornobyl </b>vych\\u00e1z\\u00ed 20. listopadu na PC a konzol\\u00edch Xbox Series X/S. Hra bude v den vyd\\u00e1n\\u00ed tak\\u00e9 sou\\u010d\\u00e1st\\u00ed p\\u0159edplatn\\u00e9ho <a href=\\"https://superparmeni.eu/blog/xbox-odhaluje-prvni-rijnovou-vlnu-her-pro-game-pass\\"><b>Xbox Game Pass</b></a>.</p><p data-block-key=\\"bbsr0\\"><b>Jak se t\\u011b\\u0161\\u00edte na nov\\u00fd d\\u00edl ze s\\u00e9rie Stalker? Dejte n\\u00e1m v\\u011bd\\u011bt n\\u00ed\\u017ee do koment\\u00e1\\u0159\\u016f. Nev\\u00e1hejte se pod\\u00edvat tak\\u00e9 na na\\u0161e posledn\\u00ed video.</b></p><embed embedtype=\\"media\\" url=\\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CxjZ13qz7Ys\\"/><p data-block-key=\\"305co\\"></p>", "id": "55fea3be-f762-4c9a-a930-041fcb6762ea"}]	21	30	stalker 2, heart of chornobyl, xbox, xbox series s, konzole, fps	\N	0	2	0
