6, "name": "Cena/Vkon", "text": "ASUS ROG Strix Scope II 96 Wireless se pohybuje v cenov kategorii nad 4 500 K a spluje oekvn kladen na pikov model. Pestoe balen nen tak rozshl jako u nkterch jinch model, jako je napklad ROG Azoth, nabz klvesnice vynikajc vkon a kvalitu. Magnetick odnmateln oprka zpst je pjemnm bonusem pro dlouh hodiny hran.", "score": 8, "review": 38}], "go_live_at": null, "like_count": 0, "main_image": 14, "read_count": 1, "draft_title": "[Recenze] ASUS ROG Strix Scope II 96 Wireless", "linked_game": null, "review_type": "Keyboard", "content_type": 55, "dislike_count": 0, "live_revision": 96, "show_in_menus": false, "latest_revision": 97, "translation_key": "afcfa6e3-e16e-46d5-be10-398f8bb36b7e", "last_published_at": "2024-08-19T18:43:27.520Z", "first_published_at": "2024-08-19T18:43:27.520Z", "search_description": "Mli jsme to poten vyzkouet si hern klvesnici ASUS ROG Strix Scope II 96 Wireless a rdi se s vmi podlme o nae prvn dojmy. Jak si tato bezdrtov krska vedla v na redakci?", "wagtail_admin_comments": [], "has_unpublished_changes": true, "latest_revision_created_at": "2024-08-19T18:44:03.857Z"}	\N	38	2	55	1	[Recenze] ASUS ROG Strix Scope II 96 Wireless
